%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20Rejects%20Canada's%20Charge%20Over%20Khalistani%20Terrorist%20Killing%3A%2010%20Facts%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Col%3E%20%3Cli%3EPrime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20said%20his%20government%20had%20%26quot%3Bcredible%20allegations%26quot%3B%20linking%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar's%20killing%20in%20June%20last%20year%20with%20the%20%26quot%3Bagents%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20India%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BCanadian%20security%20agencies%20have%20been%20actively%20pursuing%20credible%20allegations%20of%20a%20potential%20link%20between%20agents%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20and%20the%20killing%20of%20a%20Canadian%20citizen%2C%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%26quot%3B%20Trudeau%20told%20an%20emergency%20session%20of%20the%20parliament%20today.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EThe%20Indian%20government%20said%20the%20allegations%20made%20by%20the%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20were%20%26quot%3Bcompletely%20rejected.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BSuch%20unsubstantiated%20allegations%20seek%20to%20shift%20the%20focus%20from%20Khalistani%20terrorists%20and%20extremists%2C%20who%20have%20been%20provided%20shelter%20in%20Canada%20and%20continue%20to%20threaten%20India's%20sovereignty%20and%20territorial%20integrity%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20foreign%20ministry%20statement.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3ETrudeau%20said%20his%20government%20has%20declared%20its%20concerns%20to%20Indian%20security%20and%20intelligence%20officials.%20He%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20he%20had%20discussed%20the%20matter%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20during%20his%20India%20trip%20for%20G20%20this%20month.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BAny%20involvement%20of%20a%20foreign%20government%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20a%20Canadian%20citizen%20on%20Canadian%20soil%20is%20an%20unacceptable%20violation%20of%20our%20sovereignty.%20It%20is%20contrary%20to%20the%20fundamental%20rules%20by%20which%20free%2C%20open%2C%20and%20democratic%20societies%20conduct%20themselves%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20the%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3ETrudeau%20said%20his%20government%20is%20working%20closely%20with%20its%20allies%20on%20this%20%26quot%3Bvery%20serious%20matter%26quot%3B%20and%20also%20sought%20India's%20cooperation.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EHardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%20who%20headed%20the%20Khalistani%20Tiger%20Force%20and%20the%20Canadian%20arm%20of%20Sikhs%20For%20Justice%20(SFJ)%2C%20was%20shot%20dead%20by%20unknown%20attackers%20near%20a%20gurdwara%20in%20Surrey%20in%20June%20last%20year.%20A%20designated%20terrorist%20in%20India%2C%20he%20was%20born%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3ELast%20July%2C%20the%20Indian%20anti-terror%20agency%20had%20announced%20a%20cash%20reward%20of%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20on%20Nijjar%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20murder%20of%20a%20Hindu%20priest%20in%20Jalandhar%2C%20Punjab.%20It%20is%20also%20probing%20the%20recent%20attacks%20on%20Indian%20diplomatic%20missions%20in%20Canada%2C%20UK%20and%20US.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3ECanada%20has%20been%20among%20the%20favoured%20hubs%20of%20expat%20Sikhs%20where%20extremism%20has%20mushroomed%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years.%20The%20past%20few%20months%20saw%20multiple%20Khalistani%20activities%20in%20Canada%2C%20including%20protests%20outside%20the%20Indian%20Embassy%20and%20threat%20posters%20for%20Indian%20diplomats.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EPM%20Modi%20conveyed%20concern%20over%20%26quot%3Bcontinuing%20anti-India%20activities%20of%20extremist%20elements%20in%20Canada%26quot%3B%20during%20a%20bilateral%20meeting%20with%20Trudeau%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20G20%20summit%20in%20Delhi%20this%20month.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695091380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-11%2F8kr7u6is_justin-trudeau-reuters_625x300_16_November_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcanada-pm-accuses-india-over-khalistani-terrorists-killing-10-facts-4402635%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20has%20reje