'%20Factor%20-%20An%20Issue%20For%20India%20Or%20Distraction%20For%20Trudeau%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20K%20word%20has%20long%20been%20associated%20with%20Kashmir%20for%20India%20in%20geopolitics%20and%20diplomacy%20but%20now%20another%20K%20-%20Khalistan%20-%20has%20emerged%20as%20vastly%20contentious%2C%20souring%20ties%20between%20India%20and%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20latest%20statement%20that%20is%20sure%20to%20raise%20hackles%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20has%20accused%20the%20Indian%20government%20of%20involvement%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20pro-Khalistan%20activist%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar.%20Trudeau%20made%20the%20statement%20in%20the%20House%20of%20Commons%20as%20the%20Canadian%20parliament%20convened%20on%20Monday%2C%20%26quot%3BAny%20involvement%20of%20a%20foreign%20government%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20a%20Canadian%20citizen%20on%20Canadian%20soil%20is%20an%20unacceptable%20violation%20of%20our%20sovereignty%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20as%20reported%20by%20Canadian%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EForeign%20Minister%20Melanie%20Joly%20later%20announced%20that%20Canada%20had%20also%20expelled%20a%20top%20Indian%20diplomat%20over%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20comes%20just%20a%20week%20after%20Trudeau%20made%20a%20reference%20to%20%26quot%3Binterference%26quot%3B%20while%20in%20Delhi%20for%20the%20G20%20Summit.%20He%20had%20alleged%20Indian%20interference%20in%20Canada.%20While%20talking%20about%20his%20meeting%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20India%20having%20raised%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20Khalistan%2C%20Trudeau%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BDiaspora%20Canadians%20make%20up%20a%20huge%20proportion%20of%20our%20country%2C%20and%20they%20should%20be%20able%20to%20express%20themselves%20and%20make%20their%20choices%20without%20interference%20from%20any%20of%20the%20many%20countries%20that%20we%20know%20are%20involved%20in%20interference%20challenges.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20statement%20released%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20after%20the%20Modi-Trudeau%20meeting%20said%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20had%20conveyed%20%26quot%3Bstrong%20concerns%20about%20continuing%20anti-India%20activities%20of%20extremist%20elements%20in%20Canada.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENijjar%20was%20killed%20outside%20a%20gurudwara%20on%20June%2018%20in%20Surrey%20in%20British%20Columbia.%20Nijjar%20was%20a%20known%20Khalistan%20backer%20and%20since%20his%20killing%20by%20two%20masked%20gunmen%2C%20his%20supporters%20have%20been%20accusing%20India%20of%20a%20role%20though%20no%20evidence%20was%20produced.%20After%20posters%20inciting%20violence%20had%20pictures%20of%20Indian%20diplomats%2C%20including%20India's%20High%20Commissioner%20to%20Canada%2C%20Sanjay%20Kumar%20Verma%2C%20the%20former%20consul%20general%20of%20India%20in%20Toronto%2C%20Apoorva%20Srivastava%2C%20and%20the%20Consul%20General%20of%20India%20in%20Vancouver.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EResponding%20swiftly%20to%20the%20posters%20associated%20with%20what%20was%20called%20a%20Freedom%20Rally%2C%20Melanie%20Joly%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BCanada%20takes%20its%20obligations%20under%20the%20Vienna%20Conventions%20regarding%20the%20safety%20of%20diplomats%20very%20seriously.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20two%20months%20since%2C%20the%20situation%20seems%20to%20have%20escalated%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Trudeau%20has%20indicated%20that%20his%20government%20has%20%26quot%3Bcredible%20intelligence%20inputs%20of%20the%20Indian%20government's%20involvement%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20Nijjar%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20some%20in%20Canada%20have%20called%20this%20a%20distraction%20as%20Trudeau%20faces%20a%20tough%20parliament%20session.%20Opposition%20leader%20Pierre%20Poilievre%20has%20already%20raised%20the%20issue%20of%20affordability%20and%20is%20expected%20to%20double%20down%20on%20his%20attacks%20on%20Trudeau.%20From%20a%20housing%20crisis%20to%20food%20inflation%2C%20Trudeau's%20popularity%20has%20been%20sagging.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2C%20from%202018%20to%202022%2C%20relations%20between%20the%20Modi%20government%20and%20Trudeau%20had%20worsened%20over%20the%20Khalistan%20row.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETrudeau's%202018%20visit%20to%20India%20was%20marred%20over%20the%20Khalistan%20issue%20with%20a%20major%20controversy%20breaking%20out%20over%20his%20former%20wife%20Sophie%20being%20photographed%20at%20an%20event%20in%20Mumbai%20with%20convicted%20Khalistan%20activist%20Jaspal%20Singh%20Atwal.%20It%20so%20turned%20out%20that%20Atwal%20was%20also%20invited%20to%20a%20dinner%20at%20the%20Canadian%20High%20Commission.%20The%20invite%20was%20recalled%20after%20the%20furore%20but%20the%20diplomatic%20damage%20was%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAtwal%20had%20served%2020%20years%20in%20prison%20for%20having%20tried%20to%20kill%20the%20then%20Punjab%20cabinet%20minister%20Malkiat%20Singh%20Sidhu%20in%20Vancouver%20in%201986.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20after%20Trudeau's%20support%20to%20the%20farmers'%20protest%20in%20India%2C%20an%20open%20letter%20written%20by%20a%20group%20of%20former%20India%20diplomats%20had%20accused%20the%20Canadian%20PM%20of%20indulging%20in%20vote%20bank%20politics%20by%20pandering%20to%20pro-Khalistani%20elements.%20The%20letter%20had%20said%20that%20Khalistani%20elements%20in%20Canada%20control%20a%20number%20of%20prominent%20Gurudwaras%2C%20which%20gives%20them%20access%20to%20substantial%20funds%2C%20some%20of%20which%20are%20allegedly%20diverted%20to%20the%20electoral%20campaign%20of%20political%20parties%20especially%20the%20Liberals.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20both%20domestic%20issues%20at%20play%20and%20now%20a%20risky%20entanglement%20with%20India%20over%20a%20sensitive%20issue%2C%20it%20seems%20Trudeau%20faces%20a%20tough%20fall%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Maha%20Siddiqui%20is%20a%20journalist%20who%20has%20extensively%20reported%20on%20public%20policy%20and%20gl