interest%20in%20view%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20comment%20earlier%20today%20that%20%26quot%3Bhistoric%20decisions%26quot%3B%20will%20be%20taken%20in%20this%20special%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20few%20key%20meetings%20held%20earlier%20added%20to%20the%20expectations%20--%20Commerce%20and%20Industry%20Minister%20Piyush%20Goyal%20and%20Parliamentary%20Affairs%20Minister%20Pralhad%20Joshi%20met%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20and%20BJP%20chief%20JP%20Nadda.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20speculation%20that%20the%20cabinet%20may%20clear%20anything%20from%20reservation%20for%20women%20or%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%2C%20%26quot%3BOne%20Nation%20One%20Election%26quot%3B%20and%20even%20a%20change%20of%20the%20country's%20name.%3Cbr%3E%20%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%20There%20were%20hopes%20of%20clarity%20after%20the%20meet%2C%20but%20the%20suspense%20continued%20with%20the%20government%20skipping%20the%20customary%20briefing.%20Shortly%20after%2C%20sources%20confirmed%20that%20the%20buzz%20about%20green-lighting%20the%20women's%20reservation%20bill%20was%20spot%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELater%20in%20the%20evening%2C%20Congress's%20communications%20in-charge%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20posted%20on%20X%3A%20%26quot%3BIt's%20been%20a%20long-standing%20demand%20of%20the%20Congress%20party%20to%20implement%20women's%20reservation.%20We%20welcome%20the%20reported%20decision%20of%20the%20Union%20Cabinet%20and%20await%20the%20details%20of%20the%20Bill.%20This%20could%20have%20very%20well%20been%20discussed%20in%20the%20all-party%20meeting%20before%20the%20Special%20Session%2C%20and%20consensus%20could%20have%20been%20built%20instead%20of%20operating%20under%20a%20veil%20of%20secrecy%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%2C%20drawn%20up%20in%202008%2C%20has%20been%20on%20freeze%20since%20it%20was%20passed%20by%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20in%202010.%20It%20was%20never%20presented%20in%20the%20lower%20house.%3Cbr%3E%20%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%20Though%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Congress%20have%20always%20supported%20the%20bill%2C%20there%20was%20hurdles%20in%20form%20of%20opposition%20by%20other%20parties%20and%20demands%20for%20quota%20for%20backward%20classes%20within%20the%20women's%20quota.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20Parliament%20session%2C%20leaders%20from%20the%20Opposition%20had%20pushed%20for%20women's%20reservation.%20So%20did%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar%20faction%20of%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party.%20The%20parties%20had%20made%20a%20strong%20push%20for%20it%20at%20the%20all-party%20meeting%20held%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20matter%20was%20also%20raised%20during%20Day%20One's%20proceedings%20for%20the%20Special%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECongress%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20speaking%20at%20the%20discussion%20on%20'Parliamentary%20Journey%20of%2075%20years%20Starting%20from%20Samvidhan%20Sabha%20%E2%80%93%20Achievements%2C%20Experiences%2C%20Memories%20And%20Learnings%26quot%3B%2C%20pointed%20to%20the%20skewed%20gender%20ratio%2C%20saying%20parliament%20has%20only%2014%20per%20cent%20women%2C%20and%20their%20percentage%20in%20legislative%20assemblies%20is%20just%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20BJP%20slammed%20the%20Congress%20over%20the%20issue%2C%20a%20strong%20retort%20came%20from%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party's%20Supriya%20Sule%2C%20who%20said%20she%20would%20like%20to%20%26quot%3Bset%20the%20record%20straight%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20first%20woman%20president%20of%20India%2C%20Pratibha%20Patil%2C%20was%20from%20the%20Congress%2C%20the%20first%20woman%20PM%20of%20the%20country%2C%20Indira%20Gandhi%2C%20was%20from%20the%20Congress%2C%20the%20first%20woman%20speaker%2C%20Meira%20Kumar%2C%20was%20from%20the%20Congress%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20like%20to%20put%20one%20more%20thing%20on%20record%20which%20Rakesh%20Singh%20seems%20to%20have%20missed%20out.%20The%20Women's%20Reservation%20Bill%20was%20brought%20by%20the%20Congress%2C%20unfortunately%20we%20did%20not%20have%20the%20numbers%20and%20we%20could%20not%20get%20it%20passed%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695084480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fljifo6ns_narendra-modi-cabinet-meet_625x300_18_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwomens-reservation-bill-cleared-in-key-cabinet-meeting-say-sources-4401961%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20bill%20to%20ensure%20the%20reservation%20of%2033%20per%20cent%20seats%20for%20women%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20state%20legislative%20assemblies%20was%20cleared%20by%20the%20Union%20cabinet%20this%20evening%2C%20sources%20have%20told%20NDTV.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A30%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwomens-reservation-bill-cleared-in-key-cabinet-meeting-say-sources-4401961%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwomens-reservation-bill-cleared-in-key-cabinet-meeting-say-sources-4401961%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwomens-reservation-bill-cleared-in-key-cabinet-meeting-say-sources-4401961%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22New%20Chinese%20college%20syllabus%3A%20Crash%20course%20on%20how%20to%20catch%20spies%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695084264000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103769391%2Cimgsize-49876.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fnew-addition-to-chinese-college-syllabus-crash-course-on-how-to-catch-spies%2Farticleshow%2F103769367.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20students%20flooded%20back%20into%20Beijing's%20top%20universities%20in%20early%20September%2C%20a%20propaganda%20blitz%20around%20campuses%20signalled%20an%20ominous%20addition%20to%20their%20syllabus%3A%20a%20crash%20course%20on%20how%20to%20catch%20spies.%22%2