%20Earth%20As%20ISRO%20Performs%20Key%20Manoeuvre%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAditya%20L1%20spacecraft%2C%20India's%20first%20space-based%20mission%20to%20study%20the%20Sun%2C%20got%20a%20%26quot%3Bsend-off%26quot%3B%20from%20the%20Earth%20after%20orbiting%20it%20since%20its%20September%202%20launch%20as%20it%20underwent%20a%20key%20manoeuvre%20in%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20Tuesday%2C%20ISRO%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Trans-Lagrangian%20Point%201%20Insertion%20manoeuvre%20marks%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20spacecraft's%20about%20110-day%20trajectory%20to%20the%20destination%20around%20the%20L1%20Lagrange%20point%2C%20a%20balanced%20gravitational%20location%20between%20the%20Earth%20and%20the%20Sun.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOff%20to%20Sun-Earth%20L1%20point!%20The%20Trans-Lagrangian%20Point%201%20Insertion%20(TL1I)%20manoeuvre%20is%20performed%20successfully.%20The%20spacecraft%20is%20now%20on%20a%20trajectory%20that%20will%20take%20it%20to%20the%20Sun-Earth%20L1%20point.%20It%20will%20be%20injected%20into%20an%20orbit%20around%20L1%20through%20a%20maneuver%20after%20about%20110%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20ISRO%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20fifth%20consecutive%20time%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO)%20has%20successfully%20transferred%20an%20object%20on%20a%20trajectory%20toward%20another%20celestial%20body%20or%20location%20in%20space%2C%20the%20country's%20space%20agency%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAditya-L1%20is%20the%20first%20Indian%20space-based%20observatory%20to%20study%20the%20Sun%20from%20a%20halo%20orbit%20around%20first%20Sun-Earth%20Lagrangian%20point%20(L1)%2C%20located%20roughly%201.5%20million%20km%20from%20earth%2C%20which%20is%20about%20one%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20Earth-Sun%20distance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Sun%20is%20a%20giant%20sphere%20of%20gas%2C%20and%20Aditya-L1%20would%20study%20the%20outer%20atmosphere%20of%20the%20Sun.%20It%20will%20neither%20land%20on%20the%20Sun%20nor%20approach%20the%20Sun%20any%20closer.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%20its%20launch%2C%20Aditya-L1%2C%20during%20its%20journey%20around%20the%20Earth%2C%20underwent%20four%20Earth-bound%20manoeuvres%20on%20September%203%2C%205%20%2C10%20and%2015%20respectively%2C%20during%20which%20it%20gained%20the%20necessary%20velocity%20for%20its%20further%20journey%20to%20L1.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUpon%20arrival%20at%20the%20L1%20point%2C%20another%20manoeuvre%20binds%20Aditya-L1%20to%20an%20orbit%20around%20L1.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20satellite%20spends%20its%20whole%20mission%20life%20orbiting%20around%20L1%20in%20an%20irregularly%20shaped%20orbit%20in%20a%20plane%20roughly%20perpendicular%20to%20the%20line%20joining%20the%20Earth%20and%20the%20Sun.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAditya-L1%20is%20expected%20to%20arrive%20at%20the%20intended%20orbit%20at%20the%20L1%20point%20after%20about%20127%20days%2C%20ISRO%20had%20said%20soon%20after%20the%20launch.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EISRO's%20Polar%20Satellite%20Launch%20Vehicle%20(PSLV-C57)%20on%20September%202%20successfully%20launched%20the%20Aditya-L1%20spacecraft%2C%20from%20the%20Second%20Launch%20Pad%20of%20Satish%20Dhawan%20Space%20Centre%20(SDSC)%2C%20Sriharikota.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20flight%20duration%20of%2063%20minutes%20and%2020%20seconds%20that%20day%2C%20Aditya-L1%20spacecraft%20was%20successfully%20injected%20into%20an%20elliptical%20orbit%20of%20235x19500%20km%20around%20the%20earth.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20ISRO%2C%20a%20spacecraft%20placed%20in%20the%20halo%20orbit%20around%20the%20L1%20point%20has%20the%20major%20advantage%20of%20continuously%20viewing%20the%20Sun%20without%20any%20occultation%20%2Feclipses.%20This%20will%20provide%20a%20greater%20advantage%20of%20observing%20the%20solar%20activities%20and%20its%20effect%20on%20space%20weather%20in%20real%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAditya-L1%20carries%20seven%20scientific%20payloads%20indigenously%20developed%20by%20ISRO%20and%20national%20research%20laboratories%20including%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Astrophysics%20(IIA)%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20and%20Inter%20University%20Centre%20for%20Astronomy%20and%20Astrophysics%20(IUCAA)%2C%20Pune.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20payloads%20are%20to%20observe%20the%20photosphere%2C%20chromosphere%20and%20the%20outermost%20layers%20of%20the%20Sun%20(the%20corona)%20using%20electromagnetic%20and%20particle%20and%20magnetic%20field%20detectors.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUsing%20the%20special%20vantage%20point%20L1%2C%20four%20payloads%20directly%20view%20the%20Sun%20and%20the%20remaining%20three%20payloads%20carry%20out%20in-situ%20studies%20of%20particles%20and%20fields%20at%20the%20Lagrange%20point%20L1%2C%20thus%20providing%20important%20scientific%20studies%20of%20the%20propagatory%20effect%20of%20solar%20dynamics%20in%20the%20interplanetary%20medium.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20suits%20of%20Aditya%20L1%20payloads%20are%20expected%20to%20provide%20the%20most%20crucial%20information%20to%20understand%20the%20problem%20of%20coronal%20heating%2C%20coronal%20mass%20ejection%2C%20pre-flare%20and%20flare%20activities%20and%20their%20characteristics%2C%20dynamics%20of%20space%20weather%2C%20propagation%20of%20particles%20and%20fields.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20scientists%2C%20there%20are%20five%20Lagrangian%20points%20(or%20parking%20areas)%20between%20the%20Earth%20and%20the%20Sun%20where%20a%20small%20object%20tends%20to%20stay%20if%20put%20there.%20The%20Lagrange%20Points%20are%20named%20after%20Italian-French%20mathematician%20Joseph-Louis%20Lagrange%20for%20his%20prize-winning%20paper%20--%20%26quot%3BEssai%20sur%20le%20Probl%C3%A8me%20des%20Trois%20Corps%2C%201772.%26quot%3B%20These%20points%20in%20space%20can%20be%20used%20by%20spacecraft%20to%20remain%20there%20with%20reduced%20At%20a%20Lagrange%20point%2C%20the%20gravitational%20pull%20of%20the%20two%20large%20bodies%20(the%20sun%20and%20the%20earth)%20equals%20the%20necessary%20centripetal%20force%20required%20for%20a%20small%20object%20to%20move%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695076200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F5431esu4_aditya-l1-19-sept_625x300_19_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsolar-mission-aditya-l1-gets-send-off-from-earth-as-isro-performs-key-manoeuvre-4402533%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Aditya%20L1%20spacecraft%2C%20India's%20first%20space-based%20mission%20to%20study%20the%20Sun%2C%20got%20a%20%26quot%3Bsend-off%26quot%3B%20from%20the%20Earth%20after%20orbiting%20it%20since%20its%20September%202%20launch%20as%20it%20underwent%20a%20key%20manoeuvre%20in%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20Tuesday%2C%20ISRO%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsolar-mission-aditya-l1-gets-send-off-from-earth-as-isro-performs-key-manoeuvre-4402533%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsolar-mission-aditya-l1-gets-send-off-from-earth-as-isro-performs-key-manoeuvre-4402533%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsolar-mission-aditya-l1-gets-send-off-from-earth-as-isro-performs-key-manoeuvre-4402533%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bailey%20Zimmerman%20on%20How%20His%20Heartbreak%20Anthems%20Conquered%20Country%20Radio%2C%20Broke%20Streaming%20Records%20and%20Brought%20Him%20to%20Stagecoach%E2%80%99s%20Door%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695076187000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FBZ-Press-Image-2-Credit-Spidey-Smith-e1695074033198.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235726820%22%2C%22