20a%20foreign%20government%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20a%20Canadian%20citizen%20on%20Canadian%20soil%20is%20an%20unacceptable%20violation%20of%20our%20sovereignty%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20the%20Canadian%20government%20has%20not%20made%20public%20any%20of%20the%20evidence%20it%20has%20for%20the%20claim%20of%20an%20Indian%20government%20hand%20in%20Nijjar%E2%80%99s%20killing.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJoly%E2%80%99s%20office%20said%20that%20the%20expelled%20Indian%20diplomat%20is%20Pavan%20Kumar%20Rai%2C%20identified%20by%20them%20as%20the%20head%20of%20the%20Research%20and%20Analysis%20Wing%20(RAW)%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20foreign%20intelligence%20agency%2C%20in%20Canada.%20A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocuments.doptcirculars.nic.in%2FD2%2FD02eod%2FPKRaiwsY5j.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E1997%20batch%20Indian%20Police%20Service%20officer%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20was%20posted%20to%20Ottawa%20as%20minister%20(eco%2C%20coordination%2C%20community%20affairs)%20in%20the%20Indian%20high%20commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20likely%20that%20India%20will%20also%20expel%20a%20Canadian%20diplomat%20in%20a%20reciprocal%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECBC%20News%20reported%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbc.ca%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Ftrudeau-indian-government-nijjar-1.6970498%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrudeau%20had%20already%20briefed%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20leaders%20of%20some%20of%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20closest%20allies%20about%20the%20case%2C%20including%20British%20Prime%20Minister%20Rishi%20Sunak%2C%20French%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20and%20U.S.%20President%20Joe%20Biden.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJoly%20also%20stated%20that%20she%20will%20be%20raising%20the%20assassination%20issue%20with%20her%20G7%20counterparts%20at%20the%20United%20Nations%20in%20New%20York%20on%20Monday%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThough%20there%20has%20been%20no%20official%20reaction%20yet%20from%20the%20Indian%20high%20commission%20in%20Ottawa%20or%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20in%20Delhi%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EGlobe%20and%20Mail%20%3C%2Fem%3Ereported%20that%20the%20Indian%20government%20had%20denied%20all%20responsibility%20for%20Nijjar%E2%80%99s%20shooting%20and%20was%20insisting%20that%20pro-Khalistan%20activists%20in%20Canada%20had%20misled%20Canadian%20investigators.%20The%20newspaper%20said%20it%20had%20learned%20of%20this%20Indian%20response%20from%20sources%20that%C2%A0it%20was%20unable%20to%20identify%20%E2%80%9Cas%20they%20could%20face%20prosecution%20under%20the%20Security%20of%20Information%20Act%E2%80%9D%20for%20discussing%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20June%2C%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%20who%20headed%20the%20pro-Khalistan%20outfits%20Khalistan%20Tiger%20Force%20and%20the%20Canadian%20arm%20of%20Sikhs%20For%20Justice%20(SFJ)%2C%20was%20shot%20dead%20at%20a%20parking%20lot%20of%20a%20gurdwara%20in%20Surrey%2C%20Canada.%20He%20was%20wanted%20for%20the%20shooting%20of%20a%20priest%20in%20Punjab%20and%20was%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fhardeep-singh-nijjar-killing-khalistan-speculation%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20third%20pro-Khalistan%20activist%20to%20die%20abroad%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20month%20and%20half.%20Immediately%20after%20his%20death%2C%20his%20supporters%20had%20claimed%20that%20the%20Indian%20government%20was%20behind%20the%20killing.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERelations%20between%20India%20and%20Canada%20have%20been%20tense%20over%20the%20activities%20of%20pro-Khalistian%20groups%20in%20Canada%20and%20Ottawa%E2%80%99s%20perception%20that%20New%20Delhi%20was%20interfering%20in%20its%20internal%20affairs.%20The%20meeting%20between%20Trudeau%20and%20Modi%20last%20week%20at%20the%20G20%20was%20visibly%20frosty%2C%20going%20by%20the%20scowls%20on%20display%20during%20the%20photo-op%20and%20the%20divergent%20statements%20each%20side%20issued.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20first%20time%20in%20recent%20memory%20that%20any%20foreign%20government%2C%20barring%20Pakistan%2C%20has%20directly%20accused%20New%20Delhi%20of%20being%20involved%20in%20an%20act%20of%20violence%20on%20their%20territory%2C%20let%20alone%20a%20murder.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20allegations%20that%20Indian%20security%20forces%20and%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3Eintelligence%20agents%20have%20acted%20abroad%20in%20contravention%20of%20international%20law%20have%20been%20made%20recently%20in%20two%20high%20profile%20cases.%20The%20first%20concerned%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fdubai-princess-sheikh-latifa-pegasus-list%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecapture%20and%20rendition%20of%20Sheikha%20Latifa%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20daughter%20of%20the%20ruler%20of%20Dubai%2C%20by%20Indian%20special%20forces%20on%20the%20high%20seas%20off%20Goa%20in%20March%202018%2C%20and%20the%20second%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fchoksi-kidnap-case-antigua-police-report-backs-fugitive-diamantaires-abduction-claims%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eattempted%20abduction%20of%20fugitive%20diamantaire%20Mehul%20Choksi%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Antigua%20in%20May%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98India%20must%20help%20us%20get%20to%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20matter%E2%80%99%20says%20Trudeau%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ctvnews.ca%2Fpolitics%2Fng-postpones-team-canada-trade-mission-to-india-amid-strained-relations-1.6562643%5C%22%3EGovernment%20sources%20cited%20by%20the%20%3Cspan%3E%3Ci%3EGlobe%20and%20Mail%3C%2Fi%3E%20newspaper%20in%20Canada%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20privately%20ruled%20out%20the%20severing%20of%20diplomatic%20relations%20with%20India%20but%20said%20Ottawa%20was%20considering%20measures%20to%20respond%20to%20what%20it%20considers%20a%20serious%20violation%20of%20Canadian%20sovereignty.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETrudeau%20also%20told%20Canadian%20MPs%20that%20India%20was%20urged%20%E2%80%9Cto%20get%20to%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20matter%E2%80%9D%20when%20top%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20intelligence%20and%20security%20officials%20%E2%80%9Cdeclared%20%5Btheir%5D%E2%80%93%C2%A0%20deep%20concerns%E2%80%9D%20to%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20also%20expect%20it%20(India)%20to%20reiterate%20that%20its%20position%20on%20extra-judicial%20operations%20in%20another%20country%20is%20clearly%20and%20unequivocally%20in%20line%20with%20international%20law%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20contrary%20to%20the%20fundamental%20rules%20by%20which%20free%2C%20open%2C%20and%20democratic%20societies%20conduct%20themselves.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FICFggjGgIdY%3Fsi%3Dmhg0jnDAgna4BTCd%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ETrudeau%20told%20parliament%20that%20he%20had%20already%20briefed%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20opposition%20leaders%20about%20the%20Indian%20government%E2%80%99s%20involvement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20these%20allegations%20are%20true%2C%20they%20represent%20an%20outrageous%20affront%20to%20Canada%2C%20to%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20sovereignty.%20Our%20citizens%20must%20be%20safe%20from%20extrajudicial%20killings%20of%20all%20kinds%2C%20most%20of%20all%2C%20from%20foreign%20governments%2C%E2%80%9D%20Conservative%20leader%20Pierre%20Poilievre%20was%20quoted%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3EGlobe%20and%20Mail%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20saying.%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9CCanadians%20deserve%20to%20be%20protected%20on%20Canadian%20soil.%20We%20call%20on%20the%20Indian%20government%20to%20act%20with%20utmost%20transparency%20as%20authorities%20investigate%20this%20murder%2C%20because%20the%20truth%20must%20come%20out.%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%9CLet%20us%20lock%20arms%20and%20join%20hands%20in%20condemning%20this%20murder%2C%20standing%20with%20the%20family%20and%20the%20friends%20of%20this%20victim.%20Let%E2%80%99s%20put%20aside%20our%20difference%20to%20stand%20up%20for%20the%20rule%20of%20law.%20One%20law%20for%20all%20our%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbc.ca%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Ftrudeau-indian-government-nijjar-1.6970498%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECBC%20reported%20him%20saying%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENew%20Democratic%20Party%20leader%20Jagmeet%20Singh%20reacted%20to%20Trudeau%E2%80%99s%20disclosure%20by%20saying%20the%20Modi%20government%C2%A0has%20pursued%20%E2%80%9Cdivision%2C%20violence%2C%20persecution%E2%80%9D%20and%20was%20%E2%80%9Cattacking%20those%20who%20are%20critical%E2%80%9D%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECanada%E2%80%99s%20public%20safety%20minister%20Dominic%20LeBlanc%20announced%20that%20David%20Vigneault%2C%20director%20of%20the%20Canadian%20Security%20Intelligence%20Service%2C%20and%20Trudeau%E2%80%99s%20national%20security%20adviser%2C%20Jody%20Thomas%2C%20had%20also%20recently%20visited%20India%20to%20discuss%20the%20assassination.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Canadian%20prime%20minister%20was%20in%20India%20for%20the%20G-20%20summit%2C%20during%20which%20he%20had%20short%20and%20tense%20meeting%20with%20the%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20He%20was%20the%20only%20leader%20who%20didn%E2%80%99t%20attend%20the%20official%20banquet%20hosted%20by%20the%20Indian%20president%20on%20Saturday%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20meeting%20on%20Sunday%20(September%2010)%2C%20the%20Indian%20readout%20said%20that%20Modi%20raised%20%E2%80%9Cstrong%20concerns%E2%80%9D%20over%20the%20activities%20of%20pro-Khalistan%20extremist%20groups.%20Trudeau%20told%20reporters%