%2Foinchkulgqrkychthutu%2FBHISDDressandGroomingCode_1.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edistrict's%20dress%20code%20policy%3C%2Fa%3E%20bars%20male%20students%20from%20having%20hair%20that%20extends%20past%20their%20eyebrows%20or%20earlobes%2C%20even%20if%20it%20is%20pulled%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGeorge%20has%20been%20stuck%20in%20in-school%20suspension%20(ISS)%20ever%20since%20for%20refusing%20to%20cut%20off%20his%20locs.%20After%20completing%20a%20two-week%20suspension%20last%20week%2C%20George%20returned%20to%20school%20on%20Monday%20with%20his%20twisted%20locs%20tied%20on%20top%20of%20his%20head%2C%20but%20not%20cut%20off.%20He%20was%20given%20another%20round%20of%20suspension%2C%20a%20civil%20rights%20activist%20helping%20his%20family%2C%20Dr.%20Candice%20Matthews%2C%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGeorge's%20mother%20Darresha%20told%20Insider%20that%20while%20her%20son%20is%20in%20ISS%2C%20he%20doesn't%20even%20have%20a%20proper%20chair%20to%20sit%20on.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDaryl%20is%20sitting%20on%20a%20stool%2C%20a%20stool%20in%20a%20cubby%2C%26quot%3B%20Darresha%20George%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20what%20conditions%20he's%20in.%20He's%20got%20to%20sit%20on%20the%20stool%20for%20eight%20hours%2C%20back%20hurting%2C%20and%20can't%20move.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20were%20to%20make%20my%20children%20sit%20on%20a%20stool%20for%20eight%20hours%2C%20I%20would%20have%20an%20issue%20with%20CPS%2C%26quot%3B%20Allie%20Booker%2C%20an%20attorney%20representing%20the%20George%20family%2C%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20Child%20Protective%20Services.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20so%20that's%20also%20the%20next%20step%20is%20that%20we're%20going%20to%20contact%20Child%20Protective%20Services%20because%20the%20conditions%20that%20he%20is%20in%20inside%20of%20that%20room%20are%20not%20proper.%20He%20doesn't%20even%20have%20a%20desk.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDarryl's%20mother%20said%20that%20the%20school%20does%20not%20offer%20students%20in%20ISS%20a%20cafeteria%20lunch%2C%20only%20a%20sandwich%20and%20a%20bottle%20of%20water.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20put%20him%20in%20ISS%2C%20taking%20him%20out%20of%20his%20education%2C%20stopping%20his%20education%2C%26quot%3B%20Darresha%20George%20added.%20%26quot%3BHis%20grades%20are%20falling%20because%20he's%20not%20getting%20proper%20instructions%20to%20do%20his%20work.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20district's%20communications%20director%2C%20David%20Bloom%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F09%2F14%2Fus%2Ftexas-student-locs-hair-crown-act.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20The%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20students%20in%20ISS%20are%20gathered%20in%20a%20room%20with%20a%20teacher%2C%20where%20they%20sit%20at%20desks%20separated%20by%20partitions.%20Bloom%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20Insider's%20request%20for%20clarification%20on%20the%20conditions%20in%20ISS.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBooker%20said%20that%20in%20addition%20to%20filing%20a%20report%20with%20CPS%2C%20she%20plans%20to%20file%20a%20lawsuit%20against%20the%20school%20this%20week%20for%20racial%20discrimination%20and%20violation%20of%20the%20Crown%20Act.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBloom%20told%20Insider%20that%20the%20district's%20policy%20on%20hair%20length%20does%20not%20violate%20the%20Crown%20Act.%20He%20pointed%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wfaa.com%2Farticle%2Fnews%2Fcommunity%2Frooted%2Fwhat-is-the-crown-act-texas-bill-law-what-does-it-cover%2F287-785f8951-a1f9-4b1f-921f-08a0ef95a2b9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatement%20from%20Rep.%20Rhetta%20Bowers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20championed%20the%20Crown%20Act%2C%20saying%20the%20law%20is%20not%20about%20hair%20length%20or%20hair%20color.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20George%20family%20and%20their%20supporters%20are%20not%20backing%20down.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDarryl's%20hair%20is%20spiritual%2C%20his%20hair%20is%20a%20connection%20to%20his%20ancestors.%20His%20hair%20is%20a%20connection%20to%20God%2C%26quot%3B%20Matthews%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20Darryl's%20dad's%20hair%2C%20stepdad's%20hair%2C%20and%20brother's%20hair%20is%20woven%20into%20his%20own.%20%26quot%3BSo%20cutting%20it%20off%20is%20cutting%20him%20off%20from%20them%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20going%20to%20keep%20fighting%2C%20but%20it's%20tearing%20him%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20Darresha%20George%20said.%20%26quot%3BHe's%20up%20every%20night.%20He%20has%20tears%20in%20his%20eyes%20every%20day.%20He's%20emotionally%20and%20physically%20drained%20behind%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftexas-school-suspend-black-student-locs-hair-lawyer-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695074885000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65088f61cd637c0019c72b4b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftexas-school-suspend-black-student-locs-hair-lawyer-2023-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%2017-year-old's%20mother%20says%20that%20her%20son%20has%20only%20had%20a%20stool%20to%20sit%20on%20for%20weeks%20while%20he's%20been%20in%20in-school%20suspension%20over%20his%20hair.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ggoodwin%40businessinsider.com%20(Grace%20Eliza%20Goodwin)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A22%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftexas-school-suspend-black-student-locs-hair-lawyer-2023-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20to%20Watch%20%E2%80%98The%20Masked%20Singer%E2%80%99%20Season%2010%20Online%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695073889000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2FMS-S9_EP912-Show-MB_00137_f.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22