d%20fraternity%20they%20learned%20to%20respect%20while%20studying%20at%20Vasant%20Valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYet%2C%20regrettably%2C%20it%20is%20these%20same%20values%20that%20are%20being%20undermined%20constantly%20by%20many%20within%20the%20India%20Today%20ecosystem%2C%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%20165%20students%20from%2018%20batches%20of%20Vasant%20Valley%20said%20in%20their%20letter%20to%20Aroon%20Purie%2C%20editor-in-chief%20of%20the%20news%20channels%20and%20also%20of%20%3Cem%3EIndia%20Today%3C%2Fem%3E%20newsmagazine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20was%20emailed%20to%20Purie%20on%20September%2013%2C%202023%20but%20the%20students%20have%20yet%20to%20get%20a%20reply.%20Another%20letter%20seeking%20his%20response%20to%20the%20letter%20was%20sent%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20Monday%20but%20has%20met%20with%20no%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20write%20to%20you%20today%20as%20the%20alumni%20of%20Vasant%20Valley%20School%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20students%20wrote.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20India%20Today%20Group%20are%20founders%20of%20Vasant%20Valley%20School%20and%20TV%20Today%20owns%20and%20operates%20multiple%20television%20channels%20including%20India%20Today%20and%20Aaj%20Tak.%20This%20is%20an%20association%20that%20many%20of%20us%20as%20alumni%20have%20been%20incredibly%20proud%20of%2C%20given%20India%20Today%E2%80%99s%20historical%20legacy%20in%20holding%20the%20powerful%20to%20account%20even%20during%20some%20of%20our%20country%E2%80%99s%20darkest%20days%2C%20including%20the%20Emergency%2C%20the%201984%20Delhi%20Riots%2C%20the%202002%20Gujarat%20Riots%2C%20to%20name%20just%20a%20handful%20of%20instances.%20And%20It%20is%20within%20the%20educational%20institution%20that%20you%20founded%2C%20that%20we%20learned%20and%20internalised%20our%20constitutional%20principles%20of%20freedom%2C%20justice%2C%20equality%2C%20liberty%2C%20and%20fraternity.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYet%2C%20regrettably%2C%20it%20is%20these%20same%20values%20that%20are%20being%20undermined%20constantly%20by%20many%20within%20the%20India%20Today%20ecosystem.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20added%3A%20%E2%80%9COur%20only%20ask%20%E2%80%A6%20is%20that%20as%20chairman%20and%20editor-in-chief%20of%20the%20India%20Today%20Group%2C%20you%20clamp%20down%20on%20the%20hatred%20emanating%20from%20your%20airwaves%20and%20hold%20accountable%20those%20that%20openly%20engage%20in%20communal%20polarisation%20under%20the%20garb%20of%20news%20reportage.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLet%20us%20start%20by%20saying%2C%20we%20recognise%20that%20today%E2%80%99s%20media%20landscape%20is%20shaped%20by%20ratings%20above%20all%20else.%20In%20this%20context%2C%20we%20want%20to%20make%20it%20clear%20that%20we%20are%20not%20comparing%20all%20of%20India%20Today%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20TV%20news.%20We%20recognise%20that%20even%20within%20this%20current%20climate%2C%20India%20Today%20continues%20to%20churn%20out%20some%20excellent%20journalism.%20The%20incredibly%20accurate%20Axis-My%20India%20exit%20polls%20are%20clearly%20a%20gold%20standard%20of%20psephology%2C%20yielding%20a%20phenomenal%20strike%20rate%20in%20terms%20of%20election%20predictions%20at%20both%20the%20state%20and%20Central%20levels.%20During%20the%20recent%20riots%20in%20Nuh%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Aaj%20Tak%20reporter%20Sreya%20Chatterjee%20did%20an%20entire%20segment%20on%20the%20effects%20of%20the%20riots%20in%20Gurgaon%2C%20while%20it%20was%20another%20Aaj%20Tak%20reporter%20who%20brought%20us%20initial%20visuals%20of%20the%20riot.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20students%20of%20the%20school%20said%20they%20were%20distressed%20at%20the%20way%20news%20was%20covered%20by%20the%20news%20channels%20owned%20by%20India%20Today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20it%20is%20extremely%20concerning%20to%20see%20the%20polarising%20tenor%20of%20some%20of%20India%20Today%E2%80%99s%20news%20anchors%2C%20particularly%20on%20Aaj%20Tak.%2050%2B%20panchayats%20have%20issued%20boycotts%20against%20the%20Muslim%20community%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20these%20riots.%20Bulldozer%20justice%2C%20which%20saw%201%2C200%2B%20structures%20demolished%2C%20has%20become%20the%20tool%20to%20inflict%20retribution%20against%20Muslims%20after%20any%20communal%20incident.%20Instead%20of%20questioning%20the%20establishment%20over%20this%20tactic%20which%20is%20an%20embarrassment%20to%20the%20rule%20of%20law%2C%20primetime%20anchors%20have%20often%20justified%20these%20actions%2C%20cheering%20on%20the%20deliverance%20of%20collective%20punishment.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20these%20times%2C%20we%20look%20towards%20organisations%20such%20as%20India%20Today%20to%20provide%20situational%20clarity%2C%20demand%20accountability%2C%20and%20douse%20the%20flames%20of%20communal%20hatred%2C%20rather%20than%20fanning%20its%20embers.%20Instead%2C%20we%20find%20that%20some%20of%20the%20commentary%20is%20extremely%20reductive%2C%20devoid%20of%20nuance%2C%20and%20does%20nothing%20to%20hold%20those%20in%20power%20accountable.%20It%20is%20as%20one%20of%20Aaj%20Tak%E2%80%99s%20shows%20is%20titled%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcjp.org.in%2Fcjp-issues-notice-to-aaj-tak-against-the-communally-divisive-black-white-show%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Black%20and%20White%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20raised%20issues%20of%20media%20complicity%20which%20the%20students%20claimed%20was%20exemplified%20by%20a%20Railway%20Protection%20Force%20officer%20who%20recently%20killed%20four%20innocent%20men%20on%20board%20a%20train%2C%20three%20of%20them%20based%20on%20their%20appearance%20as%20Muslims.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20officer%20justified%20his%20actions%20while%20carrying%20out%20this%20terrorist%20attack%2C%20citing%20the%20dog%20whistles%20he%20heard%20on%20news%20television.%20If%20the%20spate%20of%20communal%20incidents%20across%20the%20country%20isn%E2%80%99t%20a%20wake-up%20call%2C%20at%20least%20th