r.com%2F65089a13cd637c0019c737bd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221998%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EU.S.%20President%20Joe%20Biden.%3Cp%3EAnna%20Rose%20Layden%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20federal%20government%20could%20shut%20down%20after%20September%2030%20if%20lawmakers%20don't%20agree%20on%20a%20solution.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20shutdown%20would%20coincide%20with%20the%20first%20day%20federal%20student-loan%20payments%20are%20set%20to%20resume.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%202021%20contingency%20plan%20for%20the%20Education%20Department%20said%20federal%20loan%20servicing%20could%20be%20disrupted.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-payment-pause-is-over-interest-resuming-borrower-balances-2023-8%5C%22%3EStudent-loan%20borrowers%20are%20facing%20new%20bills%20in%20less%20than%20two%20weeks%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20could%20also%20be%20facing%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flikelihood-of-federal-government-shutdown-2023-who-is-affected-economy%5C%22%3Egovernment%20shutdown%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELawmakers%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsocial-security-benefits-student-loan-repayment-congress-funding-budget-fight-2023-8%5C%22%3Ejust%2013%20days%20to%20reach%20a%20funding%20agreement%3C%2Fa%3E%20before%20the%20government%20is%20set%20to%20run%20out%20of%20money%20on%20September%2030.%20And%20at%20this%20point%2C%20things%20aren't%20looking%20too%20good%20%E2%80%94%20a%20group%20of%20conservative%20lawmakers%20on%20Sunday%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flikelihood-of-federal-government-shutdown-2023-who-is-affected-economy%5C%22%3Eproposed%20a%20short-term%20resolution%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20would%20fund%20the%20government%20through%20October%2031%2C%20accompanied%20by%20provisions%20aimed%20at%20strengthening%20border%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDemocrats%20have%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthehill.com%2Fhomenews%2Fhouse%2F4205474-jeffries-democrats-wont-help-gop-advance-bipartisan-spending-bills%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20they%20will%20not%20support%20that%20bill%20%E2%80%94%20and%20even%20some%20House%20Republicans%20have%20expressed%20opposition%20to%20the%20resolution%2C%20meaning%20lawmakers%20have%20limited%20time%20to%20find%20an%20agreement%20that%20can%20win%20enough%20votes%20to%20pass.%20If%20not%2C%20Americans%20will%20face%20a%20government%20shutdown%20on%20October%201%2C%20which%20also%20happens%20to%20be%20the%20same%20day%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-borrowers-facing-perfect-storm-repayment-debt-relief-biden-2023-8%5C%22%3Efederal%20student-loan%20payments%20resume%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThings%20are%20already%20complicated%20enough%20for%20the%20student-loan%20industry%20without%20a%20looming%20government%20shutdown.%20Due%20to%20the%20unprecedented%20volume%20of%20borrowers%20reentering%20repayment%20at%20once%2C%20student-loan%20servicers%20have%20been%20flooded%20with%20inquires%20%E2%80%94%20and%20they%20have%20demonstrated%20they%20don't%20have%20sufficient%20resources%20to%20handle%20all%20borrowers%20who%20need%20help.%20One%20company's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-company-nelnet-call-center-website-down-debt-interest-2023-9%5C%22%3Ewebsite%20and%20call%20center%20has%20shut%20down%20repeatedly%3C%2Fa%3E%20due%20to%20technical%20errors%2C%20and%20some%20borrowers%20have%20told%20Insider%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-borrowers-uncertainty-payments-resuming-debt-relief-paperwork-issues-2023-8%5C%22%3Ethey%20have%20spent%20hours%20on%20hold%20with%20their%20servicer%20to%20no%20avail%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0All%20that%20could%20be%20much%20worse%20if%20the%20Education%20Department%20shuts%20down%20at%20the%20same%20time%20payments%20are%20supposed%20to%20start%20up.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20over%20three%20years%20on%20pause%2C%20federal%20borrowers%20will%20start%20footing%20an%20extra%20monthly%20bill%20as%20early%20as%20October%201.%20The%20Office%20of%20Management%20and%20Budget%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fomb%2Finformation-for-agencies%2Fagency-contingency-plans%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehas%20contingency%20plans%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20every%20federal%20agency%20on%20how%20they%20structure%20their%20operations%20in%20the%20event%20of%20a%20shutdown.%C2%A0However%2C%20since%20this%20payment%20resumption%20is%20unprecedented%2C%20the%20Education%20Department%20does%20not%20yet%20have%20a%20contingency%20plan%20for%20managing%20Federal%20Student%20Aid's%20operations%C2%A0without%20funding%20in%20two%20weeks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.ed.gov%2Fabout%2Fshutdown%2Fcontingency-plan-2021.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emost%20recent%20contingency%20plan%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20OMB's%20website%20for%20the%20Education%20Department%20is%20from%202021%2C%20meaning%20the%20department%20is%20currently%20reviewing%20what%20its%20new%20plan%20should%20be.%20At%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20shutdown%2C%20federal%20employees%20across%20all%20agencies%20would%20be%20furloughed%2C%20including%20nearly%20all%20of%20Education's%20staff.%20According%20to%20the%20Education%20Department's%202021%20plan%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20Department%20would%20phase%20in%20employees%20only%20as%20necessary%20to%20support%20and%20prevent%20significant%20damage%20to%20the%20underlying%20activity.%20At%20most%2C%20not%20more%20than%2011%20percent%20of%20the%20total%20staff%20would%20be%20called%20back%20to%20work%20during%20a%20longer%20interruption.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20federal%20student-loan%20program%2C%20the%202021%20plan%20stated%20that%20basic%20operations%20including%20the%20disbursement%20of%20Pell%20Grants%20and%20federal%20student%20loans%2C%20along%20with%20the%20servicing%20of%20federal%20student%20loans%2C%20%26quot%3Bcould%20continue%20for%20a%20very%20limited%20time%3B%20these%20operations%20could%20also%20experience%20some%20level%20of%20disruption%20due%20to%20a%20lapse.%26quot%3B%20So%20the%20longer%20the%20shutdown%20is%2C%20the%20more%20severe%20the%20impacts%20will%20be%20for%20student-loan%20borrowers%20who%20are%20attempting%20to%20seek%20federal%20aid%20or%20receive%20assistance%20from%20their%20loan%20servicer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESection%20124%20of%20the%20OMB's%202023%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2Fa11.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eguidance%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20executing%20the%20federal%20budget%20outlines%20how%20every%20agency%20should%20prepare%20for%20a%20lapse%20in%20appropriations.%20All%20agencies%20should%20be%20prepared%20to%20initiate%20their%20shutdown%20plans%20within%20one-half%20day%2C%20and%20they%20should%20have%20plans%20for%20a%20shutdown%20that%20extends%20for%20a%20prolonged%20period%20of%20time.%20Agencies%20also%20have%20to%20plan%20how%20they%20will%20resume%20operations%20once%20funding%20is%20restored.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Education%20Department%20has%20said%20it%20remains%20in%20frequent%20contact%20with%20servicers%20to%20ensure%20a%20smooth%20transition%20back%20into%20repayment.%20Regardless%2C%20borrowers%20are%20still%20on%20the%20hook%20for%20their%20student-loan%20bills%20next%20month%2C%20and%20it%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20how%20a%20government%20shutdown%20will%20impact%20the%20student-loan%20industry%20as%20it%20turns%20back%20on%20once%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-will-government-shutdown-affect-student-loan-payment-resumption-debt-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695064847000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65089a13cd637c0019c737bd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-will-government-shutdown-affect-student-loan-payment-resumption-debt-2023-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Congress%20has%2013%20days%20to%20fund%20the%20government.%20If%20not%2C%20the%20Education%20Department%20will%20shut%20down%20the%20same%20day%20student-loan%20payments%20resume.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22asheffey%40businessinsider.com%20(Ayelet%20Sheffey)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A30%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-will-government-shutdown-affect-student-loan-payment-resumption-debt-2023-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Characters%20to%20expect%20in%20One%20Piece%20Season%202%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695064823000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103766645%2Cimgsize-73000.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fhollywood%2Fnews%2Fwhite-hunter-to-king-wapol-characters-to-expect-in-one-piece-season-2-live-action-adaptation%2Farticleshow%2F103766651.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F103766651.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20upcoming%20Season%202%20of%20the%20live-action%20adaptation%20of%20'One%20Piece'%20will%20feature%20several%20iconic%20characters%2C%20including%20King%20Wapol%2C%20Captain%20Smoker%2C%20Dr.%20Kureha%2C%20Miss%20All%20Sunday%2C%20Crocodile%2C%20Nefertari%20Vivi%2C%20Portgas%20D.%20Ace%2C%20and%20Tony%20Tony%20Chopper.%20Fans%20are%20excited%20to%20see%20how%20these%20characters%20will%20be%20portrayed%20in%20the%20ambitious%20adaptation%2C%20which%20has%20garnered%20a%20lot%20of%20anticipation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fhollywood%2Fnews%2Fwhite-hunter-to-king-wapol-characters-to-expect-in-one-piece-season-2-live-action-adaptation%2Farticleshow%2F103766651.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rights%20Orgs%2C%20Activists%20Condemn%20Permission%20to%20NHRC%20to%20Host%20Global%20Meet%20Despite%20Accreditation%20Deferment%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2Fnhrc_pti.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Close%20to%202%2C000%20civil%20society%20organisations%20and%20individuals%20have%20signed%20a%20statement%20condemning%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20Asia%20Pacific%20Forum%20has%20granted%20the%20National%20Human%20Rights%20Commission%20of%20India%20permission%20to%20host%20its%20next%20conference%20in%20Delhi%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20a%20global%20alliance%20of%20human%20rights%20organisations%20has%20deferred%20its%20accreditation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20May%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fnhrcs-accreditation-deferred-by-global-alliance-may-lose-top-level-ranking-report%5C%22%3Ereports%20had%20noted%20that%20the%20Global%20Alliance%20of%20National%20Human%20Rights%20Institutions%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20deferred%20the%20NHRC%E2%80%99s%20accreditation%20for%20the%20second%20time%20since%20it%20was%20first%20recognised%20by%20the%20international%20body%20in%201999%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fganhri.org%2F%5C%22%3Eciting%3C%2Fa%3E%20lack%20of%20diversity%20in%20staff%20and%20leadership%2C%20political%20interference%20in%20appointments%2C%20police%20officers%E2%80%99%20involvement%20in%20investigations%20of%20human%20rights%20violations%2C%20and%20other%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20NHRC%20India%20after%20March%202023%2C%20did%20not%20have%20the%20courage%20to%20call%20for%20a%20meeting%20with%20civil%20society%20members%20to%20drawn%20up%20strategies%20in%20partnership%20with%20us%20and%20has%20instead%20used%20the%20APF%20conference%20to%20politicise%20the%20issue%20on%20the%20sidelines%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20note%20by%20the%201%2C877%20civil%20society%20organisations%20and%20individuals%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHosting%20the%2028th%20bi-annual%20APF%20conference%20at%20New%20Delhi%20on%20September%2020-21%20will%20give%20the%20NHRC%20a%20fig%20leaf%20of%20international%20legitimacy%20to%20cover%20up%20its%20dismal%20performance%2C%20the%20organisations%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20their%20detailed%20press%20release%20the%20organisations%20cite%20the%20fact%20that%20anti-terror%20laws%20such%20as%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Protection)%20Act%20have%20been%20used%20to%20target%20and%20silence%20human%20rights%20defenders%2C%20lawyers%2C%20activists%20and%20journalists%2C%20most%20prominently%20in%20the%20Elgar%20Parishad%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20release%20also%20noted%20the%20NHRC%E2%80%99s%20role%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInspite%20of%20this%20shocking%20state%20of%20affairs%20which%20threatened%20human%20rights%2C%20it%20was%20bound%20to%20protect%2C%20the%20NHRC%20was%20silent.%20The%20NHRC%20was%20roused%20from%20its%20slumber%20to%20issue%20notice%20to%20the%20state%20of%20Manipur%2C%20only%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20initiated%20suo%20motu%20action%20on%20the%20complaint%20of%20sexual%20violence%20against%20members%20of%20the%20Kuki%20Zo%20community.%20In%20one%20of%20the%20most%20serious%20human%20rights%20challenges%20in%20recent%20years%20which%20has%20dimensions%20of%20ethnic%20cleansing%2C%20sexual%20crimes%20and%20even%20possibly%20crimes%20against%20humanity%2C%20the%20response%20of%20the%20NHRC%20(belated%20and%20weak)%20has%20been%20nothing%20short%20of%20an%20abdication%20of%20its%20constitutional%20and%20legal%20responsibility.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmong%20other%20situations%20when%20it%20has%20been%20silent%20are%20when%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20state%20has%20deployed%20bulldozers%20to%20destroy%20the%20homes%20of%20Muslim%20minorities%20as%20well%20as%20dissenters%20in%20total%20violation%20of%20the%20rule%20of%20law%E2%80%9D%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Delhi%20and%20Haryana%2C%C2%A0%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20NHRC%20has%20also%20been%20silent%20with%20respect%20to%20the%20rise%20in%20vigilante%20crimes%20against%20the%20Muslim%20minority%20happening%20with%20%E2%80%9Ca%20sickening%20regularity%20throughout%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20organisations%20further%20said%2C%20noting%20also%20its%20silence%C2%A0%20when%20human%20rights%20defenders%20like%20Teesta%20Setalvad%20and%20journalists%20like%20Khurram%20Parvez%20were%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20NHRC%E2%80%99s%20own%20former%20Special%20Monitor%20Mr.%20Harsh%20Mandar%20was%20targeted%20by%20the%20government%2C%20the%20NHRC%20has%20decided%20to%20remain%20a%20silent%20spectator%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDamningly%2C%20it%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CNot%20in%20a%20single%20case%20related%20to%20journalists%20which%20were%20before%20the%20High%20Courts%20or%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20did%20the%20NHRC%20ever%20in%20the%20recent%20past%20deemed%20it%20pertinent%20to%20follow%20APF%E2%80%99s%20own%20action%20plan%20for%20protection%20of%20Human%20Rights%20Defenders%20of%20March%202022.%20The%20instances%20can%20be%20multiplied%2C%20but%20the%20simple%20point%20is%20that%20the%20NHRC%20is%20a%20silent%20spectator%20to%20the%20wilful%20destruction%20of%20both%20human%20rights%20and%20the%20rule%20of%20law%20in%20India%20today.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%C2%A0APF%20conference%20will%20be%20an%20opportunity%20to%20further%20whitewash%20the%20sins%20of%20omission%20of%20the%20NHRC%20on%20a%20global%20stage%2C%20the%20organisation%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIndia%20is%20the%20only%20country%20globally%20which%20has%20over%20170%20national%20and%20state%20thematic%20human%20rights%20institutions%20and%20we%20in%20civil%20society%20are%20deeply%20concerned%20that%20the%20hosting%20of%20this%20conference%20will%20provide%20legitimacy%20to%20an%20institution%20which%20sees%20itself%20as%20wanting%20to%20be%20a%20show%20piece%20to%20the%20external%20world%20rather%20than%20being%20the%20soul%20of%20protecting%20human%20rights%20in%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20observed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20added%20that%20the%20NHRC%20should%20meet%20the%20mandate%20conferred%20by%20the%20Protection%20of%20Human%20Rights%20Act%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Paris%20principles.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20call%20upon%20APF%20and%20all%20chairperson%20members%20of%20NHRIs%20to%20see%20through%20the%20politicization%20of%20this%20APF%20conference%20by%20one%20of%20your%20own%20members%20whose%20track%20record%20has%20been%20extremely%20poor%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20an%20indicator%20of%20its%20poor%20track%20record%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20NHRC%20has%20functioned%20without%20filling%20in%20three%20key%20positions%20for%20the%20past%20nine%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20release%20is%20signed%20by%20Henri%20Tiphagne%2C%20National%20Working%20Secretary%20of%20the%20All%20India%20Network%20of%20NGOs%20and%20Individuals%20working%20with%20National%20and%20State%20Human%20Rights%20Institutions%20(AiNNI).%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695064013000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2Fnhrc_pti.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fnhrc-asia-pacific-forum-global-meet-accreditation%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hosting%20the%2028th%20bi-annual%20APF%20conference%20at%20New%20Delhi%20on%20September%2020-21%20will%20give%20the%20NHRC%20a%20fig%20leaf%20of%20international%20legitimacy%20to%20cover%20up%20its%20dismal%20performance%2C%20the%20organisations%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22ca