C%20and%20consensus%20could%20have%20been%20built%20instead%20of%20operating%20under%20a%20veil%20of%20secrecy%2C%26quot%3B%20Ramesh%20said%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEver%20since%20it%20was%20announced%20that%20the%20Parliament%20session%20would%20be%20held%20from%20September%2018-22%2C%20there%20has%20been%20speculation%20on%20various%20bills%2C%20including%20the%20women's%20reservation%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Women's%20Reservation%20Bill%20passed%20by%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20in%202010%20had%20provision%20for%2033%20per%20cent%20reservation%20for%20women%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20state%20assemblies.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20PM%20Modi%20highlighted%20the%20changing%20composition%20of%20the%20House%20over%20the%20years%2C%20saying%20it%20had%20become%20more%20inclusive%20with%20all%20sections%20of%20society%20finding%20representation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInclusive%20atmosphere%20has%20kept%20manifesting%20the%20aspirations%20of%20the%20people%20with%20full%20power%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3Cbr%20type%3D%5C%22_moz%5C%22%3E%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695058020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fbsgmdn48_pm-modi-pti_625x300_18_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwomens-reservation-bill-what-pm-modi-said-on-women-mps-hours-before-cabinet-cleared-quota-bill-4401660%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20Monday%20said%20the%20contribution%20of%20women%20parliamentarians%20has%20been%20on%20the%20rise%20over%20the%20years%2C%20hours%20before%20the%20Union%20Cabinet%20cleared%20the%20women%20reservation%20bill.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwomens-reservation-bill-what-pm-modi-said-on-women-mps-hours-before-cabinet-cleared-quota-bill-4401660%22%2C%22cdnA