-selector-asked-about-resting-virat-kohli-rohit-sharma-before-bharat-darshan-at-world-cup-heres-his-reply-4402128%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fbcci-chief-selector-asked-about-resting-virat-kohli-rohit-sharma-before-bharat-darshan-at-world-cup-heres-his-reply-4402128%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Microsoft's%20Chief%20Product%20Officer%20Panos%20Panay%20Quits%20Company%20After%2019%20Years%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPanos%20Panay%2C%20the%20chief%20product%20officer%20at%20Microsoft%2C%20who%20oversaw%20the%20development%20of%20Surface%20devices%20and%20Windows%2011%2C%20is%20leaving%20the%20company%20after%2019%20years.%20Mr%20Panay%20announced%20his%20departure%20from%20the%20company%20via%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20tweet%2C%20he%20wrote%2C%20''After%2019%20incredible%20years%20at%20Microsoft%2C%20I've%20decided%20to%20turn%20the%20page%20and%20write%20the%20next%20chapter.%20I'm%20forever%20grateful%20for%20my%20time%20at%20Microsoft%20and%20the%20amazing%20people%20I%20had%20the%20honor%20to%20make%20products%20with.''%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESee%20the%20tweet%20here%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EAfter%2019%20incredible%20years%20at%20Microsoft%2C%20I've%20decided%20to%20turn%20the%20page%20and%20write%20the%20next%20chapter.%20I'm%20forever%20grateful%20for%20my%20time%20at%20Microsoft%20and%20the%20amazing%20people%20I%20had%20the%20honor%20to%20make%20products%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Panos%20Panay%20(%40panos_panay)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fpanos_panay%2Fstatus%2F1703776961296998693%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2018%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20internal%20email%20to%20staff%2C%20Microsoft%20Executive%20Vice%20President%20Rajesh%20Jha%20confirmed%20Mr.%20Panay's%20departure.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2023%2F09%2F18%2Fmicrosoft-product-chief-panos-panay-is-leaving-the-company.html%5C%22%3EThe%20email%20read%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20''After%20nearly%2020%20years%20at%20the%20company%2C%C2%A0Panos%20Panay%C2%A0has%20decided%20to%20leave%20Microsoft.%20Panos%20has%20had%20an%20incredible%20impact%20on%20our%20products%20and%20culture%20as%20well%20as%20the%20broader%20devices%20ecosystem.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUnder%20Panos'%20leadership%2C%20the%20team%20created%20the%20iconic%20Surface%20brand%20with%20loved%20products.%20More%20recently%2C%20as%20the%20leader%20of%20Windows%2C%20the%20team%20has%20brought%20amazing%20services%20and%20experiences%20to%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20with%20Windows%2011%20on%20innovative%20devices%20including%20those%20from%20our%20OEM%20partners.%20He%20will%20be%20missed%2C%20and%20I%20am%20personally%20very%20grateful%20for%20his%20many%20contributions%20over%20the%20years.%20Please%20join%20me%20in%20wishing%20him%20well.''%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20Mr.%20Panay%20joined%20Microsoft%20in%202004%20as%20one%20of%20the%20company's%20group%20program%20managers%20and%20became%20the%20person%20in%20charge%20of%20supervising%20the%20Surface%20hardware%20division%20as%20well%20as%20other%20products.%C2%A0He%20was%20named%20the%20company's%20chief%20product%20officer%20in%202018%20and%20was%20promoted%20to%20executive%20vice%20president%20after%20a%20successful%20Windows%2011%20launch%20in%202021.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThank%20you%2C%20Panos%2C%20for%20your%20impact%20on%20our%20products%2C%20culture%2C%20company%2C%20and%20industry%20over%20the%20past%20two%20decades.%20I'm%20grateful%20for%20your%20leadership%2C%20support%2C%20and%20all%20you've%20done%20for%20Microsoft%20and%20our%20customers%20and%20partners%2C%26quot%3B%20Microsoft%20CEO%20Satya%20Nadella%20said%20in%20an%20emailed%20statement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20per%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftechcrunch.com%2F2023%2F09%2F18%2Fchief-product-officer-panos-panay-is-out-at-microsoft%2F%5C%22%3E%20%3Cem%3ETechCrunch%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20news%20comes%20just%20days%20before%20a%20New%20York%20City%20event%20set%20to%20debut%20new%20Surface%20hardware.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMicrosoft's%20consumer%20marketing%20head%2C%20Yusuf%20Mehdi%2C%20will%20take%20over%20leading%20the%20Windows%20and%20Surface%20businesses.%20''Yusuf%20Mehdi%20will%20take%20on%20the%20responsibility%20of%20leading%20the%20Windows%20and%20Surface%20businesses%20with%20our%20OEM%20and%20Retail%20partners%2C''%20the%20memo%20reads.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695057300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fpcefn95o_microsofts-chief-product-officer-panos-panay-_625x300_18_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fmicrosofts-chief-product-officer-panos-panay-quits-company-after-19-years-4402204%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20Mr%20Panay%20said%20''he's%20decided%20to%20turn%20the%20page%20and%20write%20the%20next%20chapter.''%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fmicrosofts-chief-product-officer-panos-panay-quits-company-after-19-years-4402204%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fmicrosofts-chief-product-officer-panos-panay-quits-company-after-19-years-4402204%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fmicrosofts-chief-product-officer-panos-panay-quits-company-after-19-years-4402204%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bajaj%20set%20to%20launch%20its%20'biggest%20ever'%20Pulsar%20by%20March%2C%20says%20MD%20Rajiv%20Bajaj%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695056713000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2020-05%2F07