ion%20minister%20Prahlad%20Patel.%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWomenReservationBill%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WomenReservationBill%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FPyP0txPNmq%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FPyP0txPNmq%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Live%20Law%20(%40LiveLawIndia)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLiveLawIndia%2Fstatus%2F1703818209349275994%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2018%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMinister%20Patel%20in%20his%20post%20on%20X%20had%20written%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Conly%20the%20Modi%20government%20had%20the%20moral%20courage%20to%20fulfil%20the%20demand%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%20reservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20movement%20in%20the%20Bill%20was%20seen%20earlier%20too.%20The%20last%20iteration%20of%20the%20Bill%20was%20officially%20known%20as%20the%20Constitution%20(One%20Hundred%20and%20Eighth%20Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202008.%20First%20introduced%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20by%20the%20Manmohan%20Singh%20government%2C%20and%20passed%20by%20the%20upper%20house%20in%202010%2C%20it%20has%20not%20been%20introduced%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20it%20is%20not%20clear%20if%20this%20is%20going%20to%20be%20the%20Bill%20which%20will%20bring%20the%2033%25%20reservation%20or%20a%20new%20one%20will%20be%20introduced.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwomens-reservation-bill-cleared-in-key-cabinet-meeting-say-sources-4401961%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20government%20has%20not%20yet%20made%20an%20official%20announcement%20on%20it%20and%20also%20skipped%20the%20customary%20briefing%20after%20the%20cabinet%20meet.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMinister%20Patel%20deleted%20his%20post%20within%20an%20hour%20of%20posting%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20also%20speculation%20that%20the%20cabinet%20may%20clear%20the%20Bill%20for%20reservation%20for%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20and%20also%20push%20the%20%E2%80%98One%20Nation%20One%20Election%E2%80%99%20legislation%20in%20this%20special%20five-day%20session%20of%20the%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESeveral%20political%20parties%20had%20pushed%20for%20this%20Bill%20to%20take%20a%20position%20of%20importance%20in%20this%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20tweeted%20that%20the%20party%20welcomed%20the%20decision%20but%20was%20awaiting%20the%20details%20of%20the%20Bill.%20Ramesh%20additionally%20decried%20the%20veil%20of%20secrecy%20surrounding%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20could%20have%20very%20well%20been%20discussed%20in%20the%20all-party%20meeting%20before%20the%20Special%20Session%2C%20and%20consensus%20could%20have%20been%20built%20instead%20of%20operating%20under%20a%20veil%20of%20secrecy%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20Congress%20Working%20Committee%20has%20demanded%20that%20the%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Reservation%20Bill%20must%20be%20passed%20during%20the%20Special%20Session%20of%20Parliament.%20Here%20are%20some%20facts%20on%20the%20issue%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E1.%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20first%20introduced%20Constitution%20Amendment%20Bills%20for%20one-third%20reservation%20in%20panchayats%20and%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20(%40Jairam_Ramesh)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJairam_Ramesh%2Fstatus%2F1703279060435263616%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2017%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695055558000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F28095145%2FFxLei4UXgAI-cqM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwomens-res