tan%20for%20Climate%20Week%20and%20the%20UN's%20Climate%20Action%20Summit%2C%20drawing%20attention%20to%20the%20climate%20crisis.%20The%20summit%20aims%20to%20encourage%20governments%20to%20adopt%20new%20actions%20to%20combat%20climate%20change%20and%20meet%20the%20goals%20of%20the%20Paris%20climate%20agreement.%20UN%20Secretary-General%20Antonio%20Guterres%20will%20host%20the%20Climate%20Action%20Summit%2C%20and%20over%20100%20countries%20have%20expressed%20their%20desire%20to%20speak.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fclimate-takes-center-stage-at-un-as-global-temperatures-hit-record%2Farticleshow%2F103764935.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fclimate-takes-center-stage-at-un-as-global-temperatures-hit-record%2Famp_articleshow%2F103764935.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fclimate-takes-center-stage-at-un-as-global-temperatures-hit-record%2Famp_articleshow%2F103764935.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Entering%20the%20Temple%20of%20Democracy%20For%20the%20Last%20Time%3A%20A%20Parliament%20Journalist's%20Account%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2F26110305%2FParliament_pti.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%2025%20years%20ago%20that%20I%20first%20entered%20the%20press%20gallery%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20a%20bit%20intimidated%20and%20overwhelmed.%20I%20remembered%20the%20tall%20circular%20building%2C%20the%20high-roofed%20chamber%20of%20the%20lower%20house%2C%20and%20the%20feeling%20that%20this%20is%20where%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20prime%20minister%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20delivered%20that%20%E2%80%98Tryst%20with%20Destiny%E2%80%99%20address%20at%20the%20moment%20of%20Independence%2076%20years%20ago.%20The%20spartan%20grandeur%2C%20the%20portraits%20hanging%20from%20the%20walls%20of%20the%20circular%20corridor%2C%20and%20the%20tall%20statues%20all%20silent%20sentinels%20of%20a%20day%20long%20gone%2C%20watched%20me%20silently.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETwenty%20five%20years%20later%2C%20I%20entered%20the%20hallowed%20hall%20one%20last%20time%2C%20but%20this%20time%20as%20a%20visitor.%20The%20space%20reserved%20for%20the%20fourth%20pillar%20of%20democracy%20across%20the%20hall%20in%20the%20press%20gallery%20wore%20a%20deserted%20look%20with%20just%20a%20handful%20of%20colleagues%20present.%20But%20is%20it%20just%20journalism%20that%E2%80%99s%20been%20reduced%20to%20the%20fringes%20and%20journalists%20to%20spectators%2C%20I%20wondered.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20special%20session%20began%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20waxing%20eloquent%20about%20India%E2%80%99s%20journey%20of%20the%20past%2075%20years.%20Modi%20invoked%20his%20b%C3%AAte%20noire%20Nehru%20in%20statesmanlike%20fulsome%20praise%2C%20and%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20and%20even%20Manmohan%20Singh%20who%20has%20been%20dissed%20by%20the%20present%20dispensation%20through%20the%2010%20years%20that%20his%20government%20was%20in%20power.%20The%20five-day%20special%20session%20will%20witness%20the%20shift%20to%20the%20newly%20constructed%20parliament%20building%20on%20Ganesh%20Chaturthi%2C%20a%20day%20reserved%20for%20auspicious%20beginnings.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20might%20be%20shifting%20to%20the%20new%20building%20but%20this%20building%20will%20keep%20on%20inspiring%20the%20coming%20generation%2C%E2%80%9D%20Modi%20said.%20Quoting%20a%20sentence%20from%20the%20%3Cem%3EUpanishads%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20is%20inscribed%20on%20the%20gate%20of%20the%20new%20parliament%2C%20the%20PM%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20sages%20said%20to%20open%20the%20doors%20for%20the%20people%20and%20see%20how%20they%20attain%20their%20rights.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F31184547%2FScreenshot-2023-05-31-at-6.41.56-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F31184547%2FScreenshot-2023-05-31-at-6.41.56-PM.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F31184547%2FScreenshot-2023-05-31-at-6.41.56-PM-300x148.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F31184547%2FScreenshot-2023-05-31-at-6.41.56-PM-1024x504.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-655855%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22591%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20during%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20new%20parliament%20building%20on%20May%2028%2C%202023.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40narendramodi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20old%20parliament%20building%20built%20in%20the%20pre%20air-conditioning%20age%20with%20its%20iconic%20circular%20facade%20and%20cylindrical%20pillars%20was%20open%20and%20full%20of%20natural%20light.%20A%20cool%20breeze%20blew%20through%20the%20corridors%20even%20in%20the%20blazing%20summer.%20By%20contrast%2C%20the%20new%20building%20is%20a%20closed%20space%20with%20flat%2C%20straight%20and%20high%20insurmountable%20walls.%20The%20symbolism%20is%20hard%20to%20miss.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20building%20is%20designed%20to%20ward%20off%20an%20enemy%20attack%2C%20closed%20from%20all%20sides%20like%20a%20fort.%20But%20who%20is%20the%20enemy%20here%3F%E2%80%9D%20asked%20a%20scribe.%20%E2%80%9COur%20homes%20in%20the%20village%20are%20built%20in%20a%20somewhat%20similar%20fashion.%20High%20walls%20ensconce%20the%20house%20but%20then%20the%20difference%20is%20the%20house%20has%20a%20courtyard%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20it%20which%20is%20a%20hub%20where%20family%20members%20meet%20and%20it%20promotes%20a%20community%20feeling.%20This%20building%20here%20is%20stifling.%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20designs%20of%20the%20two%20buildings%20reflect%20the%20mindset%20of%20the%20dispensation%2C%20%E2%80%9Copen%20versus%20closed%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20another.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnew-parliament-building-no-solution-problems%5C%22%3ENew%20Parliament%20Building%20Is%20a%20Solution%20to%20Problems%20That%20Do%20Not%20Exist%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20new%20parliament%20has%20huge%20air-conditioned%20halls%20and%20no%20courtyard%20to%20mingle%20in%20or%20for%20general%20bonhomie.%20It%20has%20the%20look%20of%20a%20corporate%20office%2C%20a%20scribe%20said.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20media%20gallery%20is%20designed%20in%20a%20way%20that%20you%20can%20only%20see%20the%20backs%20of%20most%20MPs%20unlike%20the%20old%20House%20where%20all%20MPs%20were%20clearly%20visible%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20another.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98What%E2%80%99s%20inside%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECongress%20leader%20and%20three%20time%20MP%20Shashi%20Tharoor%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CMore%20then%20a%20beautiful%20building%20what%20is%20needed%20is%20what%20goes%20on%20inside%20it.%20What%20you%20need%20is%20a%20thriving%20democracy.%20I%20have%20seen%20two%20prime%20ministers.%20And%20Mr%20Modi%2C%20while%20quite%20striking%20when%20he%E2%80%99s%20present%2C%20has%20been%20absent%20quite%20a%20bit.%20In%20fact%2C%20I%20had%20calculated%20that%20in%20the%20first%20three%20years%20of%20his%20regime%2C%20he%20spent%20more%20time%20addressing%20foreign%20parliaments%20then%20in%20his%20own%20country.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESecurity%20officers%20say%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20office%20will%20be%20clearly%20off%20bounds%20and%20even%20the%20offices%20of%20MPs%20will%20be%20cordoned%20off.%20If%20true%2C%20this%20will%20be%20a%20far%20cry%20from%20the%20time%20when%20one%20could%20walk%20right%20into%20the%20office%20of%20the%20PM%20even%20as%20the%20Special%20Protection%20Group%20scowled%2C%20or%20accost%20a%20Vajpayee%20as%20he%20stepped%20out%20of%20the%20building%20and%20thrust%20a%20mic%20at%20him.%20You%20could%20also%20go%20room%20to%20room%2C%20be%20it%20of%20a%20minister%20or%20political%20party%2C%20sniffing%20for%20news.%20The%20durbar%20of%20the%20late%20BJP%20leader%20Arun%20Jaitely%20whether%20he%20was%20in%20the%20opposition%20or%20the%20Treasury%20Benches%20was%20an%20adda%20for%20journalists%20trying%20to%20make%20headway%20in%20an%20increasingly%20opaque%20dispensation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F30123153%2Fimage3-1.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F30123153%2Fimage3-1.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F30123153%2Fimage3-1-300x146.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F30123153%2Fimage3-1-1024x498.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-670619%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22584%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20new%20parliament%20building.%20Photo%3A%20PIB%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20was%20a%20time%20when%20the%20parliament%20played%20host%20to%20the%20camaraderie%20between%20journalists%20and%20MPs.%20You%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20cheekily%20breezed%20in%20late%20to%20parliament%20and%20parked%20your%20car%20in%20the%20common%20parking%20space.%20My%20favourite%20spot%20was%20the%20same%20as%20the%20Late%20Amar%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20and%20I%20often%20beat%20him%20to%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYou%20could%20also%20watch%20history%20in%20the%20making%20from%20the%20front%20row%20seats%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20media%20gallery%2C%20as%20many%20did%20when%20the%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Reservation%20Bill%20or%20the%20nuclear%20deal%20passed%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20Some%20of%20the%20fiercest%20orators%20in%20the%20house%20were%20Vajpayee%20and%20the%20late%20Sushma%20Swaraj.%20You%20dropped%20everything%20when%20they%20stood%20up%20to%20speak.%20Challenges%20were%20many%2C%20too.%20You%20often%20covered%20House%20proceedings%20till%202%20am%20on%20a%20foggy%20December%20night%20and%20were%20back%20to%20the%20temple%20of%20democracy%20by%2010%20am%20the%20next%20morning.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESix%20time%20MP%20and%20part%20time%20airline%20pilot%20Rajiv%20Pratap%20Rudy%20says%20he%20first%20became%20an%20MP%20in%201996%20and%20one%20of%20the%20chores%20he%20was%20tasked%20with%20by%20the%20Speaker%20was%20to%20take%20care%20of%20the%20parliament%E2%80%99s%20gardens.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20been%20closely%20associated%20with%20designing%20the%20gardens%20or%20reconstruction%20of%20public%20utilities%20in%20the%20building.%20My%20memories%20are%20reminiscent%20of%20a%20lot%20of%20good%20things%2C%20of%20excitement%20and%20loss%2C%20of%20creativity%20and%20hope.%20I%20am%20privileged%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20the%20change%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20while%20speaking%20like%20a%20statesman%20reminisced%20about%20parliament%E2%80%99s%20history%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20bullet%20marks%20on%20the%20solid%20stone%20exteriors%20are%20somber%20reminders%20of%20the%20attack%20on%20the%20parliament%20on%20December%2013%2C%202001.%20I%20for%20one%20was%20in%20my%20office%2C%20at%20a%20stone%E2%80%99s%20throw%20from%20the%20parliament.%20I%20got%20to%20know%20of%20the%20attack%20not%20from%20television%20but%20because%20a%20bullet%20hit%20the%20metal%20frame%20of%20my%20window%2C%20one%20foot%20away.%20Many%20colleagues%20have%20similar%20stories.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOpposition%20MPs%20fear%20the%20tradition%20of%20throttling%20the%20opposition%20and%20say%20that%20voices%20of%20dissent%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20heard%20in%20the%20new%20building%20as%20well.%20As%20TMC%20leader%20Derek%20O%E2%80%99Brien%20tweeted%2C%20%E2%80%9CGive%20me%20back%20an%20India%20where%20the%20head%20is%20held%20high%20and%20the%20mind%20is%20without%20fear.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695054621000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2F26110305%2FParliament_pti.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fparliament-new-building-journalism-politics-mps%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20old%20parliament%20building%2C%20built%20in%20the%20pre%20air-conditioning%20age%2C%20was%20open%20and%20full%20of%20natural%20light.%20By%20contrast%2C%20the%20new%20building%20is%20a%20closed%20space%20with%20flat%2C%20straight%20and%20high%20insurmountable%20walls.%20The%20symbolism%20is%20hard%20to%20miss.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fparliament-new-building-journalism-politics-mps%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UP%20Student%20Dies%20By%20Suicide%20In%20Coaching%20Hub%20Kota%2C%2025th%20Such%20Case%20This%20Year%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%2017-year-old%20medical%20aspirant%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20died%20after%20allegedly%20consuming%20poison%20at%20a%20coaching%20institute%20in%20Kota%20-%20the%20coaching%20hub%20of%20Rajasthan.%20This%20is%20the%2025th%20case%20of%20suicide%20by%20a%20coaching%20student%20in%20the%20city%20this%20