%20Ms%20Coats'%20family%20members%20believe%20it%20was%20a%20murder.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E''I%20believe%20it%20was%20murder%2C%20I%20really%20do.%20One%20of%20her%20legs%20was%20up%20in%20the%20air%20in%20a%20kicking%20position.%20That's%20not%20somebody%20who%20just%20laid%20in%20their%20bed%20and%20died''%2C%20Ms%20Coats'%20aunt%2C%20May%20Stevens%2C%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E''This%20is%20senseless%20and%20I%20want%20some%20answers%20because%20my%20daughter%20is%20gone.%20And%20it's%20not%20fair.%20I%20want%20everybody%20to%20find%20out%20who%20did%20this%20to%20her.%20She%20shouldn't%20be%20gone%2C''%20Sharon%20Coats%2C%20her%20mother%20told%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fktla.com%2Fnews%2Flocal-news%2Fsecond-model-found-dead-in-downtown-l-a-apartment%2F%5C%22%3EKTLA.%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cops%20are%20also%20working%20to%20determine%20if%20the%20two%20incidents%20are%20related%2C%20but%20have%20not%20confirmed%20any%20connection%20thus%20far.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20both%20their%20families%20believe%20that%20there%20might%20be%20a%20link%20between%20the%20deaths.%20They're%20also%20concerned%20a%20serial%20killer%20may%20be%20looking%20for%20their%20next%20target.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E''We%20just%20want%20to%20know%20what%20happened%20%E2%80%A6%20It%20just%20doesn't%20seem%20right%20%E2%80%A6%20Is%20there%20a%20correlation%20between%20these%20two%20females%3F%20Is%20there%20a%20correlation%3F%20They%20were%20both%20almost%20in%20the%20same%20area%20%E2%80%A6%20we%20need%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20this%20isn't%20something%20else%20because%20it%20just%20didn't%20seem%20right%2C''%20Ms%20Coats'%20cousin%20Sheniya%20Mason%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fabc7.com%2Fmodel-death-downtown-los-angeles-investigation-nichole-coats%2F13793806%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20%3Cem%3EABC%207%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer