%22title%22%3A%22Amidst%20Slugfest%20Over%20Hyderabad%20Merger%2C%20Film%20Trailer%20Leads%20to%20Fresh%20War%20of%20Words%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F18210918%2FScreenshot-2023-09-18-at-9.08.57-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHyderabad%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20At%20a%20time%20when%20the%20clash%20surrounding%20the%20merger%20of%20the%20erstwhile%20Hyderabad%20state%20by%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%2C%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(BRS)%20and%20the%20All%20India%20Majlis-e-Ittehadul%20Muslimeen%20(AIMIM)%2C%20has%20barely%20concluded%2C%20the%20release%20of%20the%20trailer%20of%20the%20film%20%3Cem%3ERazakar%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20sparked%20a%20fresh%20war%20of%20words%20among%20political%20leaders%20of%20Telangana%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20film%2C%20produced%20by%20BJP%20leader%20Gudur%20Narayana%20Reddy%2C%20which%20purportedly%20tells%20the%20story%20the%20%E2%80%98silent%20genocide%20of%20Hyderabad%E2%80%99%2C%20saw%20important%20political%20leaders%20from%20Telangana%2C%20notably%20Member%20of%20Parliament%20and%20former%20Telangana%20BJP%20chief%20Bandi%20Sanjay%2C%20and%20T.%20Raja%20Singh%2C%20the%20Goshamahal%20legislator%20who%20was%20suspended%20from%20the%20saffron%20party%2C%20throwing%20their%20weight%20behind%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EOn%20Saturday%2C%20September%2016%2C%20which%20the%20BJP%20celebrated%20as%20Hyderabad%20Liberation%20Day%2C%20Sanjay%2C%20who%20is%20now%20BJP%20national%20secretary%2C%20posted%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20that%20he%20had%20%E2%80%9Cgoosebumps%20watching%20the%20trailer%E2%80%9D.%20Taking%20a%20swipe%20at%20those%20who%20were%20opposing%20the%20film%2C%20he%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CLet%E2%80%99s%20engage%20with%20history%20even%20as%20there%20pseudo%20intellectuals%20try%20to%20erase%20it%20(%3Cem%3Esic%3C%2Fem%3E).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20trailer%20is%20gory.%20It%20is%20punctuated%20by%20seemingly%20bloodthirsty%20bearded%20men%2C%20pulling%20the%20%3Cem%3Ejaneu%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5Ba%20thread%20worn%20by%20Brahmins%5D%20off%20torsos%2C%20slashing%20throats%2C%20chopping%20off%20%3Cem%3Esikhas%20%3C%2Fem%3E(sacred%20locks%20of%20hair)%2C%20chants%20of%20%E2%80%98Allahu%20Akbar%E2%80%99%2C%20visuals%20of%20Mecca%2C%20and%20tossing%20onto%20a%20bayonet%20attached%20to%20an%20musket%20the%20body%20of%20what%20seems%20to%20be%20the%20representation%20of%20a%20Brahmin%20boy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAlarmed%20at%20the%20content%2C%20and%20at%20the%20possibility%20of%20rousing%20communal%20passions%20ahead%20of%20the%20elections%2C%20social%20media%20users%20tagged%20state%20information%20technology%20minister%20K.T.%20Ramarao%20and%20urged%20him%20to%20stop%20the%20film%E2%80%99s%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ETaking%20note%20of%20this%2C%20Rao%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FKTRBRS%2Fstatus%2F1703666221445714307%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Edescribed%3C%2Fa%3E%20those%20in%20support%20of%20the%20films%20as%20%E2%80%9Cbankrupt%20jokers%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%9D%20on%20X%20and%20said%20these%20people%20were%20trying%20to%20instigate%20communal%20violence%20and%20polarisation%20for%20their%20political%20agenda.%20He%20stated%20that%20the%20matter%20would%20be%20taken%20to%20the%20censor%20board%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Central%20Board%20of%20Film%20Certification%20%E2%80%93%20to%20ensure%20that%20there%20is%20no%20breach%20of%20peace%20in%20the%20Telangana.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThis%20evoked%20a%20sharp%20response%20from%20Sanjay%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbandisanjay_bjp%2Fstatus%2F1703673756223414317%5C%22%3Eretorted%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20BRS%20had%20reneged%20on%20its%20promise%20to%20celebrate%20Liberation%20Day.%20Taking%20a%20potshot%20at%20the%20minister%2C%20the%20BJP%20leader%20described%20him%20as%20%E2%80%98TwitterTillu%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20hoped%20that%20the%20Hindu%20deity%20Ganesh%20would%20%E2%80%9Cinstil%20some%20sense%20into%20%5Bhim%5D%C2%A0instead%20of%20engaging%20in%20futile%20attempts%20to%20erase%20history%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20spat%20on%20X%20drew%20reactions%20from%20supporters%20of%20both%20leaders.%20While%20some%20maintained%20that%20a%20movie%20on%20the%20atrocities%20of%20the%20Razakars%20was%20long%20overdue%20and%20a%20true%20recollection%20of%20what%20happened%20in%20the%20Nizam%E2%80%99s%20Hyderabad%2C%20others%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20movie%20was%20a%20misrepresentation%20of%20events%2C%20wrongly%20portrayed%20the%20Muslim%20community%20as%20a%20monolith%2C%20and%20was%20a%20threat%20to%20the%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20in%20Telangana.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20call%20to%20ban%20the%20film%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20stem%20from%20any%20support%20for%20Razakars%20but%20is%20a%20response%20to%20the%20concern%20of%20stereotyping%20the%20Muslim%20community%20based%20on%20the%20actions%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FRazakars%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Razakars%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20could%20potentially%20disrupt%20the%20peaceful%20atmosphere%20in%20Telangana%20through%20polarization%20%26amp%3B%20communalization%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FGUMptU0iMh%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FGUMptU0iMh%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20S.Q.Masood%20%7C%20%D9%85%D8%B3%D8%B9%D9%88%D8%AF%20(%40SQMasood)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSQMasood%2Fstatus%2F1703687737508008065%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2018%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EUnlike%20last%20year%2C%20the%20connotational%20slugfest%20over%20the%20vocabulary%20of%20Hyderabad%E2%80%99s%20merger%20became%20more%20combative%20given%20that%20Telangana%20goes%20to%20polls%20soon.%20The%20BRS%20is%20cautious%20of%20not%20trampling%20upon%20the%20painful%20memories%20of%201948%20annexation%20called%20Operation%20Polo%20and%20its%20aftermath%2C%20and%20is%20unwilling%20to%20give%20into%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20narrative%2C%20insists%20on%20calling%20the%20merger%20of%20the%20erstwhile%20princely%20state%20the%20%E2%80%9CNational%20Integration%20Day%E2%80%9D.%20Telangana%E2%80%99s%20party%20in%20power%20found%20support%20in%20the%20Owaisi%20brothers-led%20AIMIM%20that%20sought%20to%20celebrate%20October%2017%20as%20Youm-e-Qaumi%20Ekjehti%2C%20a%20day%20of%20national%20integration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ESunday%20witnessed%20AIMIM%20chief%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi%20locking%20horns%20with%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20who%20was%20in%20Hyderabad.%20Owaisi%20led%20a%20tricolour%20rally%20that%20crisscrossed%20the%20city%2C%20and%20culminated%20in%20a%20public%20meeting%20in%20an%20eidgah%2C%20where%20he%20launched%20a%20salvo%20at%20Shah%20and%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%2C%20accusing%20them%20both%20of%20lying.%20Shah%20had%2C%20earlier%20in%20the%20day%2C%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Ceverything%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20meaning%20the%20merger%20of%20Hyderabad%20%E2%80%93%20had%20been%20done%20without%20any%20bloodshed.%20The%20Hyderabad%20parliamentarian%20said%20that%20Nehru%20had%20made%20a%20similar%20comment%20on%20All%20India%20Radio%20on%20September%2018%2C%201948.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EOwaisi%20also%2C%20however%2C%20said%20that%20he%20would%20have%20felt%20suffocated%20if%20he%20was%20born%20during%20the%20Nizam%E2%80%99s%20rule%20as%20the%20Asaf%20Jahi%20dynasty%20was%20rooted%20in%20feudalism%2C%20and%20without%20the%20constitutional%20values%20of%20democracy%2C%20liberty%20and%20fraternity.%20He%20distanced%20himself%20from%20the%20razakars%2C%20and%20reiterated%20that%20they%20went%20to%20Pakistan%2C%20and%20those%20who%20were%20%3Cem%3Ewafadars%3C%2Fem%3E%20(patriots)%2C%20chose%20to%20stay%20in%20India.%20His%20party%20had%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20a%20previous%20manifestation%20of%20the%20organisation%2C%20he%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20word%20%E2%80%98razakar%E2%80%99%2C%20loosely%20translated%2C%20means%20%E2%80%98volunteer%E2%80%99.%20Led%20by%20Qasim%20Razvi%20the%20razakars%20were%20a%20feared%2C%20violent%20militia%20of%20the%20Majlis-e-Ittehadul%20Muslimin%2C%20popularly%20known%20as%20Ittehad.%20The%20Ittehad%20came%20into%20existence%20in%201927%2C%20and%20one%20of%20its%20tallest%20leaders%20was%20Bahadur%20Yar%20Jung%2C%20who%20later%20fell%20out%20with%20the%20last%20Nizam%2C%20Mir%20Osman%20Ali%20Khan.%20His%20sudden%20death%20in%201944%20saw%20Razvi%20taking%20over%20the%20Itthad%E2%80%99s%20reigns%20and%20steering%20it%20on%20the%20path%20of%20communalism.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EHistorian%20Inukonda%20Thirumali%20writes%20in%C2%A0%3Cem%3EAgainst%20Dora%20and%20Nizam%20People%E2%80%99s%20Movement%20in%20Telangana%201939-1948%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20this%20militia%20primarily%20comprised%20%E2%80%9Cmarginalised%20individuals%20like%20drivers%2C%20shopkeepers%20and%20unemployed%20youth%20in%20Marathwada%20region%E2%80%9D.%20Razvi%2C%20he%20writes%2C%20encouraged%20these%20individuals%20to%20%E2%80%9Crob%20and%20loot%20food%20grains%20in%20and%20around%20Latur%20in%20the%20early%201940s%E2%80%9D.%20A%20few%20years%20later%2C%20the%20razakar%20numbers%20swelled%2C%20with%20the%20then%20Diwan%20of%20Hyderabad%20Mirza%20Ismail%20referring%20to%20the%20militia%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cwretched%20band%20of%20foolish%20Muslims%20called%20the%20Ittehadul%20Muslimeen%E2%80%9D.%20As%20their%20numbers%20grew%2C%20Thirumali%20writes%20that%20Razvi%20gave%20up%20his%20civilian%20clothes%20for%20a%20military%20uniform.%20Such%20was%20the%20delusion%20of%20Razvi%20that%20he%20dreamed%20of%20flyi