der%20of%2021%3Cspan%3E%3Csup%3Est%3C%2Fsup%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20century%20who%20is%20bothy%20physically%20and%20metaphysically%20inclined.%20Why%20do%20we%20say%20this%3F%20Because%20he%20is%20the%20only%20man%20in%20recent%20history%20who%20resembles%20the%20greatest%20political%20philosopher%20and%20mystic%20of%20all%20time%2C%20Grigori%20Rasputin%2C%20in%20both%20appearance%20and%20adeptness%20at%20intrigue.%20So%20complete%20is%20the%20imitation%20that%20he%20is%20the%20only%20modern%20leader%20who%20has%20shown%20the%20courage%20to%20sport%20a%20long%20beard%20in%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F18193835%2Fmodi-rasputin.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22700%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F18193835%2Fmodi-rasputin.jpg%20700w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F18193835%2Fmodi-rasputin-300x257.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-673562%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ENarendra%20Modi%20(left)%3B%20Grigori%20Rasputin%20(right).%20Photos%3A%20TV%20grab%2FWikimedia%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20our%20country%2C%20Lenin%E2%80%99s%20goatee%20was%20an%20apology%20for%20a%20beard.%20Stalin%20only%20grew%20a%20moustache%20while%20neither%20Khrushchev%20nor%20Brezhnev%2C%20not%20to%20speak%20of%20Chernenko%2C%20Andropov%20and%20Gorbachov%2C%20could%20claim%20to%20possess%20any%20kind%20of%20stubble.%20My%20own%20leader%2C%20President%20Putin%2C%20of%20course%2C%20is%20clean%20shaven%20but%20that%20is%20because%20he%20is%20beyond%20such%20trivial%20hirsutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20I%20do%20wish%20to%20remind%20my%20Indian%20friends%20that%20for%20many%20years%2C%20Russia%20did%20not%20think%20India%20had%20acquired%20genuine%20freedom%20because%20neither%20Gandhi%20nor%20Nehru%2C%20nor%20Bose%2C%20nor%20Patel%2C%20nor%20Ambedkar%20cared%20to%20grow%20a%20beard.%20It%20takes%20extraordinary%20courage%20and%20extraordinary%20depth%20of%20character%20for%20a%20man%20in%20public%20life%20to%20sport%20a%20beard.%20Of%20course%2C%20our%20good%20friend%20Manmohan%20Singh%20also%20had%20a%20beard%2C%20but%20that%20was%20a%20religious%20obligation%2C%20not%20a%20conscious%20choice.%20Though%20he%20has%20trimmed%20it%20now%2C%20only%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20has%20chosen%20to%20make%20a%20statement%20with%20his%20beard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20ladies%20and%20gentlemen%2C%20do%20join%20me%20in%20saluting%20Modi%2C%20a%20man%20with%20courage%20to%20grow%20a%20beard.%20None%20of%20us%20knows%20what%20a%20%3Cem%3Evishwaguru%3C%2Fem%3E%20looks%20like%2C%20but%20as%20someone%20trained%20in%20Marxism%2C%20I%20dare%20say%20it%20is%20no%20dialectical%20mystery.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3EAll%20gurus%20must%20have%20a%20beard.%20Only%20Modi%20has%20a%20beard.%20QED.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EPresident%20Biden%20(United%20States)%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20Gentlemen%2C%20I%20have%20been%20around%20for%20a%20very%2C%20very%20long%20time%20and%20I%20have%20come%20across%20leaders%20of%20all%20shades%20and%20hues%20in%20almost%20every%20part%20of%20the%20world.%20I%20have%20rarely%20met%20a%20man%20so%20wonderfully%20focused%20on%20selling%20himself%20as%20Narendra%20Modi.%20In%20my%20country%2C%20especially%20in%20Middle%20America%2C%20the%20highest%20praise%20is%20reserved%20for%20the%20second-hand%20car%20salesman.%20This%20job%20requires%20cunning%2C%20sleight%20of%20hand%20%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3Eand%20a%20glib%20tongue%20since%20you%20are%20often%20selling%20shoddy%20goods%20to%20someone%20who%20does%20not%20even%20need%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20believe%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20is%20the%20World%E2%80%99s%20Greatest%20Second-hand%20Car%20Salesman%20%E2%80%93%20of%20the%20Global%20South%2C%20of%20course.%20I%20hesitate%20to%20anoint%20him%20the%20greatest%20salesman%20in%20the%20world%20because%20he%20faces%20very%20tough%20competition%20from%20my%20predecessor%20in%20the%20White%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EPrime%20Minister%20Sunak%20(UK)%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20If%20pressed%20to%20choose%20a%20salutation%2C%20I%20shall%20call%20him%20the%20greatest%20transactional%20man.%20Britain%20has%20conventionally%20been%20known%20as%20a%20nation%20of%20traders%2C%20and%20we%20do%20know%20how%20to%20strike%20a%20bargain%3B%20we%20know%20how%20to%20gauge%20the%20customer%E2%80%99s%20needs%20and%20ego%20and%20to%20adjust%20our%20sales%20pitch%20accordingly.%20But%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20is%20the%20supreme%20personification%20of%20all%20these%20qualities.%20I%20would%20have%20liked%20to%20call%20him%20the%20greatest%20transactional%20leader%20of%20all%20times%20but%20my%20team%20tells%20me%20that%20he%20is%20not%20without%20chinks%20in%20his%20armour%20%E2%80%93%20that%20it%20is%20easy%20to%20sell%20him%20anything%20as%20long%20we%20take%20care%20to%20satisfy%20his%20ego.%20We%20do%20not%20judge.%20We%20just%20do%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EPremier%20Li%20Qiang%20(China)%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20The%20Chinese%20side%20is%20very%20fond%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20because%20he%20is%2C%20if%20you%20pardon%20my%20bluntness%2C%20a%20man%20of%20straw.%20After%20his%20first%20encounter%20with%20Modi%20in%20Ahmedabad%2C%20Comrade%20Xi%20told%20the%20politburo%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20expected%20to%20meet%20a%20man%20of%20steel%2C%20but%20he%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20man%20of%20rusted%20iron.%E2%80%9D%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3EAfter%20the%20meeting%20in%20Bali%2C%20Comrade%20Xi%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3Etold%20us%3A%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20rusted%20iron%20man%20is%20becoming%20brittle%3B%20all%20too%20ready%20to%20crumble.%20What%20we%20need%20to%20do%20is%20%3Cspan%3E%E5%86%8D%E6%8E%A8%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%8B%3C%2Fspan%3E%20or%20%E2%80%93%20to%20use%20a%20Hindi%20phrase%20Mr%20Modi%20may%20know%2C%20%3Cem%3Eek%20dhakka%20aur%20do%3C%2Fem%3E%20(give%20it%20another%20push).%20I%20am%20sorry%20if%20my%20Indian%20hosts%20feel%20disappointed%20and%20I%20do%20apologise%20most%20profusely%3B%20but%20Comrade%20Xi%20has%20always%20impressed%20upon%20Chinese%20diplomats%20that%20it%20is%20better%20to%20be%20frank%20than%20to%20be%20deceitful.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EChancellor%20Olaf%20Scholz%20(Germany)%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20In%20this%20private%20gathering%2C%20I%20have%20no%20hesitation%20in%20stating%20that%20the%20man%20would%20have%20been%20very%20well%20understood%20and%20admired%20by%20people%20in%20our%20country%20%E2%80%93%20but%2080%20years%20ago.%20Because%20we%20have%20good%20reason%20to%20believe%20that%20he%20is%20only%20leader%20in%20the%20world%20whose%20nationalism%20mirrors%20the%20ideas%20of%20a%20certain%20book%20that%2C%20frankly%2C%20most%20Germans%20today%20would%20throw%20in%20the%20trash.%20What%20is%20more%2C%20he%20remains%20unfazed%20when%20he%20is%20accused%20of%20shielding%20bigots%20and%20now%20is%20planning%20for%20where%20India%20will%20be%20after%201%2C000%20years.%20Of%20course%2C%20the%20last%20leader%20who%20tried%20to%20do%20that%20with%20his%20country%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20disaster.%20Let%20me%20say%20no%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EPresident%20Macron%20(France)%3C%2Fb%3E%3A%20We%20in%20the%20French%20establishment%20take%20considerable%20pride%20in%20our%20underhandedness.%20We%20know%20how%20to%20hustle.%20We%20can%20cut%20a%20deal%20with%20any%20leader%20on%20his%20terms%20yet%20laugh%20our%20way%20to%20the%20bank.%20I%20was%20particularly%20struck%20by%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20street%20smartness%3B%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3Eimagine%2C%20declaring%20the%20adoption%20of%20the%20G20%20joint%20statement%20even%20before%20the%20rest%20of%20us%20had%20a%20chance%20to%20formally%20say%20so.%20That%20is%20a%20sort%20of%20trick%20one%20practices%20in%20party%20platforms%20but%20it%20required%20a%20special%20deviousness%20to%20do%20this%20at%20an%20international%20gathering.%20The%20art%20of%20presenting%20a%20fait%20accompli%20is%20not%20just%20a%20European%20trick.%20Monsieur%20Modi%20had%20mastered%20it.%20He%20is%20a%20master%20of%20simulacra%20and%20simulation%2C%20to%20borrow%20the%20the%20title%20of%20Baudrillard%E2%80%99s%20classic%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EPresident%20Lula%20(Brazil)%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20I%20am%20too%20much%20of%20a%20man%20of%20the%20masses%20to%20be%20taken%20in%20by%20Dear%20Leaders%2C%20wherever%20they%20may%20be.%20I%20have%20suffered%20and%20endured%20indignities%20and%20imprisonment.%20But%20I%20see%20no%20harm%20in%20giving%20in%20to%20the%20Indian%20delegation%E2%80%99s%20request%20that%20I%20exercise%20my%20discretion%20as%20the%20next%20chair%20to%20declare%20that%20the%20G20%20in%20New%20Delhi%20was%20the%20greatest%20show%20ever.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3ENo%20country%20can%20possibly%20hope%20to%20put%20up%20a%20tent%20like%20PM%20Modi%20did.%20We%20hope%20to%20host%20the%202024%20summit%20with%20a%20much%2C%20much%20smaller%20budget%20since%20we%20have%20other%20pressing%20priorities.%20I%20believe%20I%20am%20not%20being%20very%20original%20when%20I%20say%20Modi%20is%20the%20greatest%20event%20manager%20in%20the%20world%20today%2C%20%3Ci%3Eo%20melhor%20empres%C3%A1rio!%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F18195448%2Fthe-busy-showman-harpers-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221014%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F18195448%2Fthe-busy-showman-harpers-1.jpg%201014w%2C%20https%3A%2F%