p%3EMoved%20deeply%20by%20this%20incident%2C%20Manjit%20converted%20his%20bicycle%20into%20a%20%E2%80%98bird%20ambulance%E2%80%99.%20With%20this%2C%20he%20has%20treated%201%2C160%20birds%20so%20far.%20He%20even%20ensures%20that%20birds%20who%20die%20are%20given%20a%20proper%20burial%2C%20totalling%20to%201%2C280%20avians%20like%20pigeons%2C%20crows%2C%20parrots%2C%20and%20turtle%20doves%20in%20Chandigarh.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ERefused%20Bank%20Job%20for%20Environment%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20BA%20dropout%2C%20Manjit%20initially%20worked%20as%20a%20drawing%20teacher%20in%20a%20private%20school.%20Through%20the%20school%2C%20he%20came%20in%20contact%20with%20the%20same%20local%20NGO%20that%20motivated%20him%20to%20do%20social%20work.%20Then%2C%20to%20do%20his%20bit%20to%20reduce%20the%20rising%20air%20pollution%2C%20Manjit%20switched%20to%20riding%20a%20bicycle%20in%201990%20at%20the%20age%20of%2021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%201999%2C%20after%20his%20marriage%2C%20Manjit%20quit%20his%20job%20at%20the%20school%20to%20dedicate%20himself%20entirely%20to%20the%20environment.%20As%20a%20side%20hustle%2C%20he%20worked%20as%20a%20painter%2C%20but%20his%20in-laws%20were%20concerned.%20They%2C%20however%2C%20managed%20to%20get%20him%20a%20job%20offer%20as%20a%20bank%20clerk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20job%20offered%20me%20triple%20the%20income%20from%20what%20I%20was%20earning.%20But%20I%20had%20to%20refuse%20it.%20I%20did%20not%20want%20to%20get%20trapped%20in%20a%20regular%20job%20in%20a%20corporate%20world%20where%20I%20would%20have%20to%20compromise%20on%20my%20mission%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fmanjit-singh-1-1695045280.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22To%20do%20his%20bit%20to%20reduce%20the%20rising%20air%20pollution%2C%20Manjit%20switched%20to%20riding%20a%20bicycle%20in%201990%20and%20later%20dedicated%20himself%20to%20saving%20birds.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fmanjit-singh-1-1695045280.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fmanjit-singh-1-1695045280-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fmanjit-singh-1-1695045280-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fmanjit-singh-1-1695045280-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fmanjit-singh-1-1695045280-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330217%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETo%20do%20his%20bit%20to%20reduce%20the%20rising%20air%20pollution%2C%20Manjit%20switched%20to%20riding%20a%20bicycle%20in%201990%20and%20later%20dedicated%20himself%20to%20saving%20birds.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20recounts%20how%20his%20decision%20would%20often%20lead%20to%20arguments%20between%20him%20and%20his%20wife%20as%20she%20also%20worried%20about%20his%20health%20due%20to%20constant%20exposure%20to%20probable%20avian%20diseases.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20when%20she%20saw%20how%20truly%20dedicated%20I%20was%20to%20my%20cause%20and%20how%20much%20social%20acceptance%20I%20received%20with%20it%2C%20she%20eventually%20came%20on%20board%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Manjit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EManjit%2C%20who%20is%20also%20known%20as%20Prince%20Mehra%2C%20continued%20to%20spread%20awareness%20about%20air%20pollution%20till%202011%20before%20his%20visit%20to%20the%20Ferozepur%20army%20camp.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20coming%20back%20to%20Chandigarh%2C%20he%20printed%20out%20some%20pamphlets%20requesting%20citizens%20of%20Chandigarh%20to%20contact%20him%20if%20they%20spot%20an%20injured%20or%20dead%20bird.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20then%2C%20he%20had%20transformed%20his%20bicycle%20into%20a%20bird%20ambulance.%20%E2%80%9CSoon%20after%2C%20people%20started%20contacting%20me%20and%20reporting%20the%20dead%20or%20injured%20birds%20in%20their%20localities.%20I%20was%20so%20happy%20to%20see%20people%20approaching%20me.%20And%20when%20I%20was%20able%20to%20free%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F170005%2Fmumbai-indian-railway-bird-animal-rescue%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einjured%20pigeon%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20treat%20it%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20I%20was%20so%20satisfied%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20a%20sense%20of%20contentment%2C%20Manjit%20started%20getting%20recognition%20for%20his%20work.%20In%202015%2C%20his%20name%20was%20also%20listed%20in%20the%20Limca%20Book%20of%20Records%20for%20saving%20thousands%20of%20birds%20in%20Chandigarh.%20The%20same%20year%2C%20he%20was%20also%20awarded%20by%20the%20Chandigarh%20government%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20Republic%20Day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20more%2C%20even%20the%20locals%20started%20referring%20to%20him%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98bird%20man%E2%80%99!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20this%20work%2C%20I%20get%20job%20satisfaction%20as%20well%20as%20recognition.%20I%20am%20truly%20very%20content%20with%20it.%20My%20children%20take%20pride%20in%20my%20work%20when%20their%20schools%20invite%20me%20as%20a%20chief%20guest%2C%20and%20when%20their%20peers%20appreciate%20my%20work%20circulated%20in%20the%20media%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fmanjit-singh-1695045324.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Manjit%20was%20awarded%20by%20the%20Chandigarh%20government%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20Republic%20Day.%C