0the%20lead.%20In%20the%20event%2C%20they%20were%20felled%2C%20along%20with%20the%20DSP%2C%20by%20the%20initial%20volley%20from%20the%20militants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20militants%20are%20advantaged%20by%20the%20forested%20redoubt%2C%20a%20methodical%20operation%20is%20currently%20on%20to%20eliminate%20them.%20The%20RR%20is%20leveraging%20firepower%2C%20as%20it%20closes%20the%20loop%20of%20the%20cordon%20in%20a%20glacial%20manoeuvre%20designed%20to%20deny%20the%20militants%20any%20further%20terrain%20advantage.%20Yet%2C%20it%20is%20curious%20the%20RR%20is%20taking%20this%20long.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20possible%20the%20RR%20was%20lured%20into%20an%20ambush%20by%20planted%20intelligence.%20That%20the%20initial%20volley%20of%20shots%20accounted%20for%20a%20police%20officer%20shows%20that%20a%20red-hot%20lead%20was%20being%20followed%20up%2C%20post-haste.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20possibility%20is%20lent%20credence%20in%20the%20claim%20of%20The%20Resistance%20Front%20%E2%80%93%20which%20is%20but%20a%20morphed%20Lashkar-e-Tayyaba%20outfit%20%E2%80%93%20that%20the%20ambush%20was%20to%20avenge%20the%20recent%20assassination%20of%20a%20militant%20leader%20across%20the%20Line%20of%20Control%20(LC).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApparently%2C%20Indian%20intelligence%20operations%20have%20drawn%20blood%2C%20accounting%20for%20some%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Flashkar-terrorist-riyaz-ahmad-alias-abu-qasim-shot-dead-inside-mosque-rawalkot-pok-2433231-2023-09-09%5C%22%3Efour%3C%2Fa%3E%20militant%20leaders%20killed%20though%20in%20midst%20of%20their%20sanctuary%20across.%20Close%20as%20the%20ambush%20was%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20the%20latest%20assassination%2C%20the%20timing%20lends%20their%20claim%20plausibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fed7coxVUi1U%3Fsi%3Dnt8XuA98N_Sck3as%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20incident%20may%20well%20have%20been%20an%20opportunity%20ambush.%20Sometimes%20things%20do%20go%20awry%20in%20operations%2C%20not%20necessarily%20due%20to%20complacence%20but%20%E2%80%93%20as%20the%20doyen%20of%20strategists%2C%20Clausewitz%2C%20has%20put%20it%20%E2%80%93%20the%20play%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.researchgate.net%2Fpublication%2F233068942_%2527Shadows_of_Uncertainty%2527_Clausewitz%2527s_Timeless_Analysis_of_Chance_in_War%5C%22%3EChance%3C%2Fa%3E.%20As%20all%20who%E2%80%99ve%20been%20in%20a%20firefight%20well%20know%2C%20the%20hobby%20of%20the%20capricious%20God%20of%20War%20is%20to%20play%20dice%20with%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20is%20no%20second-guessing%20the%20tactical-level%20leaders%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20the%20operation%20does%20appear%20unduly%20prolonged.%20It%20flies%20in%20the%20face%20of%20the%20adage%2C%20%E2%80%98there%20is%20no%20obstacle%20for%20the%20infantry.%E2%80%99%20The%20RR%20is%20but%20infantry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20inconceivable%20that%20the%20troops%20are%20not%20straining%20at%20the%20bit%20and%20operational-level%20commanders%20are%20so%20risk%20averse%20as%20to%20continue%20reining%20them%20in%20for%20so%20long%2C%20unless%20acting%20on%20instructions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHas%20the%20military%20leadership%20been%20instructed%20by%20its%20political%20master%20to%20hold%20back%20for%20longer%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%2C%20purveyed%20on%20television%2C%20seized%20national%20attention.%20It%20had%20the%20potential%20to%20put%20a%20question%20mark%20on%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20Kashmir%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDid%20the%20regime%20unfurl%20the%20%E2%80%98Mission%20Accomplished%E2%80%99%20banner%20too%20soon%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClearly%2C%20the%20problem%20in%20Kashmir%20and%20of%20Kashmir%20has%20not%20gone%20away%2C%20even%20if%20Art