%20Manesar%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EHas%20the%20poster%20boy%20of%20Hindu%20right%20wing%20hate%20and%20violence%20been%20thrown%20%E2%80%98under%20the%20bus%E2%80%99%20by%20the%20BJP%3F%20Does%20he%20represent%20a%20%E2%80%98use%20and%20throw%E2%80%99%20policy%20being%20followed%20by%20the%20Sangh%20%E2%80%93%20exploiting%20the%20infamy%20of%20a%20Monu%20Manesar%20for%20years%2C%20embracing%20and%20legitimising%20him%20and%20his%20violence%2C%20reaping%20the%20political%20and%20electoral%20benefits%20of%20the%20hate%20being%20spread%20by%20him%20and%20his%20cohorts%20that%20polarises%20the%20nation%20and%20even%20shielding%20him%20from%20the%20law%20for%20as%20long%20as%20possible%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20then%2C%20as%20the%20violence%20gets%20to%20the%20point%20of%20%E2%80%98far%20too%20horrific%E2%80%99%20(the%20brazen%20burning%20alive%20of%20Junaid%20and%20Nasir)%2C%20becoming%20indefensible%20even%20for%20iron-plated%20stomachs%20of%20his%20benefactors%2C%20he%20is%20jettisoned%20as%20a%20face-saver%3F%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20answer%20is%20in%20between.%20There%20is%20an%20element%20of%20%E2%80%98use%20and%20throw%E2%80%99%2C%20but%20there%20is%20also%20a%20charade%20being%20played%20out%2C%20as%20we%20shall%20see%20below.%20As%20for%20Manesar%2C%20he%20knew%20what%20he%20signed%20up%20for.%20For%20decades%2C%20most%20political%20parties%20have%20engaged%20with%20criminal%20elements%2C%20used%20their%20local%20muscle%20power%20and%20%E2%80%98fear%20factor%E2%80%99%2C%20in%20some%20cases%20even%20used%20their%20unaccounted-for%20wealth%2C%20to%20gain%20and%20wield%20political%20power%20on%20the%20ground%20and%20win%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20Manesar%2C%20that%20was%20the%20template%2C%20with%20a%20communal%20tweak%20%E2%80%93%20use%20his%20%E2%80%98gau%20raksha%E2%80%99%20vigilantism%20to%20gain%20local%20notoriety%20and%20clout%3B%20tap%20into%2C%20and%20further%20vitiate%20the%20climate%20of%20hate%20against%20Muslims%3B%20rub%20shoulders%20with%20Hindu%20right-wing%20leadership%3B%20and%20hope%20to%20be%20rewarded%20%E2%80%93%20maybe%20a%20sought%20after%20post%20in%20the%20VHP-Bajrang%20Dal-BJP%20ecosystem%2C%20perhaps%20an%20MLA%20ticket%20sometime%20later%2C%20and%20so%20on.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20were%20%E2%80%98success%20stories%E2%80%99%20he%20may%20have%20wanted%20to%20emulate%20%E2%80%93%20Yati%20Narsinghanand%2C%20the%20priest%20of%20Dasna%20Mandir%20in%20Ghaziabad%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20whose%20anti-Muslim%20vitriol%20perhaps%20earned%20him%20the%20title%20of%20Mahamandaleshwar%20by%20the%20Juna%20Akhara%20%E2%80%93%20India%E2%80%99s%20biggest%20and%20most%20influential%20sadhu%20Akhara%20%E2%80%93%20in%202021.%20He%20repaid%20by%20upping%20his%20hate%20speech%20quotient.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F01%2F23010830%2FScreenshot-2022-01-23-at-1.07.34-AM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221008%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F01%2F23010830%2FScreenshot-2022-01-23-at-1.07.34-AM.png%201008w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F01%2F23010830%2FScreenshot-2022-01-23-at-1.07.34-AM-300x168.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-577338%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22563%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EScreenshot%20of%20viral%20video%20in%20which%20a%20policeman%20in%20seen%20smiling%20as%20he%20issues%20a%20summons%20to%20Hindutva%20militant%20Yati%20Narsinghanand%20for%20hate%20speech.%20Photo%3A%20X%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20%E2%80%98role%20model%E2%80%99%20may%20have%20been%20Kapil%20Mishra%2C%20infamous%20for%20standing%20next%20to%20a%20senior%20Delhi%20cop%20in%20February%202020%20and%20threatening%20violence%20in%20North-East%20Delhi%20just%20hours%20before%20bloody%20communal%20riots%20actually%20broke%20out.%20Mishra%20has%20repeatedly%20made%20inflammatory%20speeches%20on%20social%20media%20and%20in%20public%20since%20joining%20the%20BJP%20in%202019.%20In%20August%202023%2C%20he%20was%20made%20a%20vice%20president%20of%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Delhi%20unit.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Elet%E2%80%99s%20also%20examine%20how%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3EHindu%20right%20wing%20leadership%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ehas%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Edeal%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Et%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ewith%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eother%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eradical%20vigilantes%20and%20social%20media%20%E2%80%98stars%E2%80%99%20like%20Monu%20Manesar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20when%20they%20turned%20%E2%80%98too%20hot%20to%20handle%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Do%20the%20FIRs%20and%20arrests%2C%20and%20the%20denial%20and%20the%20disowning%20that%20follows%20ring%20true%2C%20or%20is%20there%20a%20pattern%20here%20that%20reveals%20a%20charade%3F%20A%20charade%20of%20%E2%80%98allowing%E2%80%99%20the%20law%20to%20%E2%80%98take%20its%20own%20course%E2%80%99%2C%20but%20actually%20being%20ineffectual.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20instance%2C%20Bittu%20Bajrangi%2C%20arrested%20on%20August%2015%2C%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20Nuh%20violence%2C%20was%20promptly%20disowned%20by%20the%20VHP.%20A%20day%20after%20his%20arrest%2C%20VHP%20wrote%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20that%20Bajrangi%20had%20%E2%80%9Cnever%20been%20associated%20with%20Bajrang%20Dal%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20the%20content%20of%20his%20videos%20%E2%80%9Cwas%20not%20appropriate%E2%80%9D.%20It%20was%20stressed%20that%20Bajrangi%20headed%20his%20own%20group%2C%20the%20Gau%20Raksha%20Bajrang%20force.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EW%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eas%20this%20a%20wilful%20%E2%80%98use%20and%20deny%E2%80%99%20policy%2C%20or%20just%20the%20fig%20leaf%20of%20%E2%80%98plausible%20deniability%E2%80%99%20since%20he%20had%20run%20afoul%20of%20the%20law%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fharyana-violence-mewat-hate-and-provocative-videos%5C%22%3EHaryana%20Violence%3A%20How%20Provocative%20Videos%20and%20a%20Background%20of%20Hate%20Preceded%20the%20Nuh%20Riots%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBajrangi%20was%20granted%20bail%20just%2015%20days%20after%20his%20arrest%2C%20paltry%20compared%20to%20the%20over%201000%20days%20Umar%20Khalid%20has%20spent%20behind%20bars%2C%20simply%20because%20he%20was%20arrested%20under%20the%20draconian%20UAPA.%20Narsinghanand%20too%2C%20arrested%20in%20January%202022%2C%20after%20calling%20for%20the%20killing%20of%20Muslims%20at%20a%20so-called%20Dharam%20Sansad%20in%20Haridwar%20in%20December%202021%2C%20was%20granted%20bail%20in%20less%20than%20a%20month%20despite%20the%20grave%20charges%20against%20him.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theweek.in%2Fwire-updates%2Fnational%2F2023%2F04%2F09%2Fbom13-gj-hate-speech-arrest.html%5C%22%3EKajal%20Hindustani%20was%20similarly%20%E2%80%98disowned%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20VHP%20in%20early%20April%202023%2C%20after%20being%20named%20in%20an%20FIR%20for%20making%20inflammatory%20speeches%20that%20contributed%20to%20communal%20violence%20in%20Gujarat%E2%80%99s%20Unain%20March.%20But%20before%20this%20denial%2C%20Kajal%20Hindustani%2C%20with%20her%20signature%20catchy%20%E2%80%98hate%20poems%E2%80%99%20was%20a%20sought%20after%20figure%20at%20radical%20Hindutva%20public%20events%2C%20with%20a%20massive%20social%20media%20following.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%202022-23%2C%20s%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ehe%20was%20seen%20at%20several%20Sakal%20Hindu%20Samaj%20rallies%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20where%20she%20even%20shared%20the%20stage%20with%20BJP%20MPs%20and%20MLAs.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EKajal%20too%20got%20bail%20within%20days%20of%20her%20arrest.%20She%20continues%20to%20post%20hate%20laden%20vitriol%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERambhakt%20Gopal%2C%20the%20so-called%E2%80%99%20Jamia%20University%20shooter%E2%80%99%2C%20who%20shot%20at%20a%20group%20of%20anti-CAA%20protestors%20in%20January%202020%2C%20injuring%20one%20student%2C%20could%20be%20described%20as%20a%20case%20of%20%E2%80%98use%2C%20deny%20and%20reuse%E2%80%99.%20At%20the%20time%20of%20the%20incident%2C%20the%20Bajrang%20Dal%20denied%20having%20any%20links%20with%20him.%20Praveen%20Bhati%2C%20a%20Bajrang%20Dal%20leader%20from%20west%20UP%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CHe%20is%20not%20a%20primary%20member%20of%20Bajrang%20Dal..%20We%20condemn%20his%20act..%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3EBut%20after%20his%20release%2C%20these%20denials%20were%20forgotten%20and%20Gopal%20has%20since%20been%20%E2%80%98re-used%E2%80%99%20by%20the%20Hindutva%20ecosystem.%20He%20has%20spoken%20at%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emahapanchayats%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20has%20posted%20visuals%20on%20social%20media%20brandishing%20guns%20and%20harassing%20Muslims%20with%20weapons.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EWatch%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fground-report-how-junaid-and-nasir-were-killed-by-cow-vigilantes%5C%22%3EGround%20Report%3A%20How%20Junaid%20and%20Nasir%20Were%20Killed%20by%20%E2%80%98Cow%20Vigilantes%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20would%20also%20help%20to%20look%20at%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EChandan%20Gupta%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ea%20case%20of%20%E2%80%98use%20and%20forget%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Gupta%20was%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ean%20Akhil%20Bharatiya%20Vidyarthi%20Parishad%20(ABVP)%20activist%20who%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fchandan-gupta-abvp-tiranga-yatra-yogi-adityanath%5C%22%3Ekilled%20in%20violence%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20a%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98T%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3Eiranga%20yatra%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(flag%20march)%20on%20January%2026%2C%202018%20in%20Kasganj.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ehis%20death%20was%20%E2%80%98used%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20he%20was%20lionised%2C%20UP%20state%20ministers%20visited%20his%20home%20and%20attended%20his%20cremation.%20A%20%E2%80%98chowk%E2%80%99%20was%20announced%20in%20his%20name%20at%20Kasganj.%20But%20in%202021%20his%20family%20staged%20a%20protest%20in%20Lucknow%2C%20claiming%20that%20Chandan%20had%20been%20forgotten.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20claimed%20that%20h%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eis%20sister%20was%20given%20a%20government%20job%20but%20it%20was%20scrapped%20within%20six%20months.%20Chandan%E2%80%99s%20incomplete%20bust%20sits%20covered%20with%20plastic%20at%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Echowk%20that%20was%20to%20be%20named%20after%20him.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20family%20says%20that%20n%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eo%20minister%20has%20had%20the%20time%20to%20inaugurate%20it%20over%20the%20last%205%20years.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20no%20%E2%80%98reuse%E2%80%99%20value%2C%20Chandan%20was%20bound%20to%20be%20forgotten.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20pattern%20that%20emerges%20goes%20roughly%20like%20this%20%E2%80%93%20first%2C%20exploit%2C%20lionise%2C%20patronise%2C%20shield%20and%20reward.%20Second%2C%20when%20the%20excesses%20get%20unpalatable%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20deny%2C%20disown%20and%20a%20mild%20rap%20on%20the%20knuckles%20in%20the%20form%20of%20toothless%20FIRs%2C%20bail%20within%20days%2C%20cases%20that%20drag%20on%20or%20collapse%20over%20time.%20Third%2C%20where%20possible%2C%20rehabilitate%20and%20reuse.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20possible%20that%20Monu%20Manesar%E2%80%99s%20case%20may%20play%20out%20differently%2C%20and%20defeat%20the%20cynicism%20in%20the%20analysis%20above.%20For%20now%2C%20we%E2%80%99ll%20just%20have%20to%20wait%20and%20watch.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERohit%20Khanna%20is%20a%20journalist%20and%20video%20storyteller.%20He%20has%20been%20Managing%20Editor%20at%20The%20Quint%2C%20and%20is%20a%20two-time%20Ramnath%20Goenka%20award%20winner.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695045966000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F23164055%2F2EC978D3-90C7-460D-AE0F-2F02A3393076.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fwas-monu-manesar-a-part-of-bjps-use-and-throw-charade-or-something-more%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Let%E2%80%99s%20examine%20how%20the%20Hindu%20right%20wing%20leadership%20has%20dealt%20with%20other%20radical%20vigilantes%20and%20social%20media%20%E2%80%98stars%E2%80%99%20like%20Manesar%2C%20when%20they%20turned%20%E2%80%98too%20hot%20to%20handle'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fwas-monu-manesar-a-part-of-bjps-use-and-throw-charade-or-something-more%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22No%20'median%20line'%20in%20Taiwan%20Strait%3A%20China%20asserts%20after%20sending%20103%20warplanes%20around%20Taiwan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695045841000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103762188%2Cimgsize-190642.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fno-median-line-in-taiwan-strait-china-asserts-after-sending-103-warplanes-around-taiwan%2Farticleshow%2F103762200.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%