1994%20season%20established%20him%20as%20one%20of%20the%20best%20players%20in%20the%20country.%20Shortly%20after%20the%20season%2C%20he%20got%20a%20call%20to%20play%20for%20the%20Indian%20National%20Team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIM%20Vijayan%E2%80%99s%20rise%20from%20poverty%20to%20stardom%20is%20a%20story%20for%20the%20books.%20As%20a%20child%2C%20he%20sold%20eatables%20in%20the%20Thrissur%20Corporation%20stadium%2C%20ironically%2C%20the%20same%20place%20that%20shaped%20his%20passion%20for%20the%20game%20and%20his%20career%20thereafter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVijayan%E2%80%99s%20love%20for%20football%20was%20spotted%20by%20Mr%20M%20K%20Joseph%2C%20the%20former%20DGP%20of%20Kerala%2C%20who%20took%20to%20the%20boy%20and%20adopted%20him%20into%20the%20Kerala%20Police%20%E2%80%94%20where%20the%20former%20started%20his%20club%20career%20in%201989.%20The%20rest%20is%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20list%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F318215%2Fdelhi-boxer-rohit-tokas-won-bronze-medal-commonwealth-games-2022-despite-knee-injuries%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egreat%20personalities%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20football%20would%20be%20incomplete%20without%20the%20name%20of%20S%20A%20Rahim.%20This%20%E2%80%98Architect%20of%20Modern%20Football%E2%80%99%20led%20the%20team%20to%20gold%20medals%20at%20the%201951%20and%201962%20Asian%20Games%2C%20along%20with%20moulding%20many%20players.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20teacher-turned-football%20coach%20is%20also%20credited%20with%20starting%20football%20groups%20across%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20some%20of%20which%20are%20still%20functional%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20these%20men%20made%20their%20mark%20on%20the%20field%2C%20Arjuna%20Award%20(1983)%20and%20Padma%20Shri%20(1985)%20awardee%20PT%20Usha%20made%20it%20on%20the%20track.%20She%20was%20only%2012%20years%20of%20age%20when%20she%20began%20training%20in%20the%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Sports%20Department%2C%20set%20up%20by%20the%