r%20the%20land.%20There%20is%20no%20connect%20between%20the%20Kashmiri%20people%20and%20the%20present%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDulat%20also%20said%20he%20has%20no%20doubt%20that%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20Inter-Services%20Intelligence%20and%20army%20are%20behind%20what%E2%80%99s%20happening%20and%20added%20that%20it%20cannot%20happen%20without%20Pakistan%20army%20chief%20Gen.%20Munir%E2%80%99s%20knowledge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEndorsing%20a%20view%20forcefully%20put%20by%20former%20chief%20minister%20Farooq%20Abdullah%20%E2%80%93%20perhaps%20as%20many%20as%20five%20times%20in%20recent%20weeks%20%E2%80%93%20that%20we%20cannot%20hope%20to%20end%20the%20violence%20and%20terror%20in%20Kashmir%20without%20talking%20to%20Pakistan%2C%20Dulat%20suggested%20that%20if%20the%20government%20is%20unwilling%20to%20talk%20to%20a%20caretaker%20regime%20in%20Islamabad%20it%20can%20speak%20to%20the%20army%20chief%20directly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20all%2C%20the%20ceasefire%20that%20came%20into%20operation%20in%202021%20was%20a%20result%20of%20national%20security%20advisor%20Ajit%20Doval%E2%80%99s%20contacts%20and%20talks%20with%20then-army%20chief%20Gen.%20Bajwa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDulat%20said%20he%20did%20not%20agree%20with%20the%20Northern%20Army%20commander%E2%80%99s%20recently%20made%20assertion%20that%20terrorists%20have%20not%20crossed%20the%20Line%20of%20Control%20but%20come%20over%20the%20border%20in%20Punjab%20or%20Nepal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20it%20was%20hard%20to%20accept%20that%20terrorists%20could%20travel%20from%20Nepal%20to%20Kokernag.%20He%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20on%20Saturday%2C%20after%20the%20Baramulla%20incident%2C%20an%20army%20brigadier%20had%20contradicted%20the%20Northern%20Army%20commander.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClearly%2C%20Dulat%20was%20suggesting%2C%20even%20the%20army%20itself%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20accept%20what%20the%20Northern%20Army%20commander%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20am%20only%20giving%20you%20the%20big%20broad%20points.%20Each%20of%20the