ir%20spokespersons%2C%20panelists%20and%20representatives%20to%20participate%20in%20programmes%20featuring%20Aman%20Chopra%2C%20Amish%20Devgan%20and%20Anand%20Narasimhan%20of%20News%2018%3B%20Chitra%20Tripathi%20and%20Sudhir%20Chaudhary%20of%20Aaj%20Tak%3B%20Gaurav%20Sawant%20and%20Shiv%20Aroor%20of%20India%20Today%3B%20Prachi%20Parashar%20of%20India%20TV%3B%20Arnab%20Goswami%20of%20Republic%20Bharat%3B%20Rubika%20Liyaquat%20of%20Bharat%2024%3B%20Navika%20Kumar%20and%20Sushant%20Sinha%20of%20Times%20Now%20Navbharat%3B%20Aditi%20Tyagi%20of%20Bharat%20Express%3B%20and%20Ashok%20Shrivastav%20of%20DD%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20sharply%20reacted%20to%20the%20decision%20and%20accused%20the%20partners%20of%20gagging%20the%20media%20with%20a%20mindset%20reminiscent%20of%20the%20emergency%20era.%20It%20also%20accused%20them%20of%20targeting%20the%20anchors%20by%20disclosing%20their%20names%2C%20thus%20making%20them%20vulnerable%20to%20physical%20attacks%20from%20those%20who%20might%20be%20actuated%20by%20the%20attitude%20of%20the%20alliance%20partners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENBDA%E2%80%99s%20odd%20response%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20News%20Broadcasters%20and%20Digital%20Association%20(NBDA)%20in%20a%20statement%20described%20the%20alliance%E2%80%99s%20decision%20as%20%E2%80%9Ca%20dangerous%20precedent%E2%80%9D%20and%20went%20on%20to%20observe%20that%20%E2%80%9CThe%20ban%20on%20representatives%20of%20the%20opposition%20alliance%20from%20participating%20in%20TV%20news%20shows%20anchored%20by%20some%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20top%20TV%20news%20personalities%20goes%20against%20the%20ethos%20of%20democracy.%E2%80%9D%20The%20usage%20of%20the%20word%20%E2%80%9Cban%E2%80%9D%20in%20its%20statement%20is%20contrary%20to%20the%20decision%20of%20the%20alliance%20partners%20not%20to%20send%20their%20representatives%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20programmes%20anchored%20by%20those%2014%20anchors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20NBDA%20also%20very%20strangely%20hailed%20those%20anchors%20as%20%E2%80%9CIndia%E2%80%99s%20top%20TV%20news%20personalities%E2%80%9D%2C%20without%20in%20any%20way%20explaining%20the%20reasons%20for%20doing%20so.%20In%20its%20statement%2C%20the%20NBDA%20remarked%20that%20the%20decision%20of%20the%20alliance%20partners%20%E2%80%9Cbetokens%20intolerance%20and%20imperils%20press%20freedom%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6betrays%20callous%20disregard%20for%20democracy%E2%80%99s%20most%20fundamental%20tenet%20%E2%80%93%20the%20inalienable%20right%20to%20openly%20express%20ideas%20and%20opinions%E2%80%9D.%20It%20also%20charged%20them%20of%20taking%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20nation%20back%20to%20the%20Emergency%20era%2C%20when%20the%20press%20was%20gagged%2C%20and%20independent%20opinions%20and%20voices%20were%20crushed%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EWatch%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Watch%20%7C%20Boycott%20of%20'Godi'%20Anchors%20Raises%20Moral%20Concerns%2C%20INDIA%20Alliance%20Needs%20a%20More%20Subtle%20Approach%3A%20N%20Ram%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fwatch-boycott-of-godi-anchors-raises-moral-concerns-india-alliance-needs-a-more-subtle-approach-n-ram%5C%22%3EBoycott%20of%20%E2%80%98Godi%E2%80%99%20Anchors%20Raises%20Moral%20Concerns%2C%20INDIA%20Alliance%20Needs%20a%20More%20Subtle%20Approach%3A%20N%20Ram%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%E2%80%99s%20record%20of%20boycotting%20TV%20channels%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20political%20parties%20have%20decided%20not%20to%20send%20their%20representatives%20to%20certain%20TV%20channels.%20There%20have%20been%20earlier%20examples%20of%20the%20BJP%20boycotting%20NDTV%20prior%20to%20Gautam%20Adani%20taking%20over%20the%20TV%20channel.%20Celebrated%20media%20personality%20N.%20Ram%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DbBNk4YLkECM%5C%22%3Ein%20an%20interaction%20with%20Karan%20Thapar%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%20been%20consistently%20boycotting%20all%20TV%20channels%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20It%20is%20worth%20noting%20that%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20boycott%20is%20not%20based%20on%20any%20formal%20announcement.%20However%2C%20it%20is%20instructive%20that%20nobody%20has%20commented%20against%20the%20BJP%20for%20doing%20so%20in%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20the%20NBDA%20has%20come%20down%20on%20INDIA%E2%80%99s%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGandhi%20appealed%20for%20boycotting%20newspapers%20spreading%20hate%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBe%20that%20as%20it%20may%2C%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20partners%20decided%20not%20to%20send%20their%20representatives%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20news%20programmes%20hosted%20by%2014%20anchors%20primarily%20because%20they%20used%20hate-filled%20remarks%20in%20a%20calculated%20manner%20in%20their%20newsrooms%20to%20engage%20in%20poisonous%20propaganda%20for%20promoting%20a%20communal%20agenda.%20Those%20partners%20did%20not%20want%20to%20be%20part%20of%20that%20agenda%20aimed%20at%20creating%20communal%20division%20and%20inciting%20religious%20sentiments%20which%20eventually%20would%20tear%20apart%20the%20unity%20and%20solidarity%20of%20people%20regardless%20of%20the%20faiths%20they%20pursued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20decision%20of%20the%20alliance%20partners%20echoes%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%201926%20appeal%20to%20people%20to%20stay%20away%20from%20newspapers%20which%20carried%20hate-filled%20content%20and%20wrought%20havoc%20to%20communal%20harmony.%20It%20is%20illuminating%20to%20note%20he%20issued%20that%20appeal%20for%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6purging%20the%20atmosphere%20of%20mutual%20hatred%20and%20calumny%E2%80%9D%2C%20by%20%E2%80%9Cboycotting%20papers%20which%20foment%20hatred%20and%20spread%20misrepresentation%E2%80%9D.%20He%20persuasively%20put%20forth%20that%20%E2%80%9CIndia%20would%20lose%20nothing%20if%2090%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20papers%20were%20to%20cease%20today%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20did%20so%20while%20moving%20a%20resolution%20on%20December%2026%2C%201926%20at%20the%20Gauhati%20session%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%2C%20expressing%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6horror%20and%20indignation%20at%20the%20cowardly%20and%20treacherous%20murder%20of%20Swami%20Shraddhanand%E2%80%9D%20and%20placing%20%E2%80%9Con%20record%20its%20sense%20of%20the%20irreparable%20loss%20the%20nation%20has%20sustained%20by%20the%20tragic%20death%20of%20a%20brave%20and%20noble%20patriot%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESwami%20Shraddhanand%20was%20assassinated%20in%20the%20last%20week%20of%20December%201926%20by%20one%20Abdul%20Rashid%20who%20came%20to%20interview%20Swamiji%20about%20his%20understanding%20of%20Islam.%20Rashid%20asked%20for%20some%20water%20to%20drink%20before%20the%20commencement%20of%20the%20interview.%20As%20Swami%E2%80%99s%20servant%20went%20to%20fetch%20water%2C%20Rashid%20took%20out%20his%20revolver%20and%20fatally%20fired%20at%20him.%20Gandhi%20took%20a%20stand%20that%20the%20hate%20and%20hostility%20spread%20by%20the%20newspapers%20in%20the%20name%20of%20religion%20deeply%20poisoned%20Rashid%E2%80%99s%20mind.%20In%20his%20article%20%E2%80%9CShraddhanandji-%20The%20Martyr%E2%80%9D%20published%20in%20%3Cem%3EYoung%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20December%2030%2C%201926%2C%20he%20wrote%20about%20the%20role%20played%20by%20newspapers%20in%20disrupting%20communal%20harmony%20by%20spreading%20hate%20and%20violence.%20Those%20words%20of%20Gandhi%20assume%20enormous%20significance%20in%20the%20context%20of%20India%20of%202023%20witnessing%20a%20demonic%20upsurge%20in%20religious%20polarisation%20caused%2C%20among%20others%2C%20by%20TV%20channels%2C%20or%20%E2%80%98Godi%20media%E2%80%99%2C%20incessantly%20peddling%20poisonous%20narratives%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20religion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGandhi%20forcefully%20asserted%20in%20the%20aforementioned%20article%20that%20%E2%80%9CThe%20newspaper%20man%20has%20become%20a%20walking%20plague%E2%80%9D%20and%20claimed%2C%20%E2%80%9CHe%20spreads%20the%20contagion%20of%20lies%20and%20calumnies.%E2%80%9D%20He%20further%20observed%2C%20%E2%80%9CHe%20exhausts%20the%20foul%20vocabulary%20of%20his%20dialect%2C%20and%20injects%20his%20virus%20into%20the%20unsuspecting%2C%20and%20often%20receptive%20minds%20of%20his%20readers%E2%80%9D.%20Gandhi%20then%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9CLeaders%20%E2%80%98intoxicated%20with%20the%20exuberance%20of%20their%20own%20language%E2%80%99%20have%20not%20known%20to%20put%20a%20curb%20upon%20their%20tongues%20or%20pens%E2%80%9D.%20He%20remarked%20with%20pain%20and%20anguish%2C%20%E2%80%9CSecret%20and%20insidious%20propaganda%20has%20done%20its%20dark%20and%20horrible%20work%2C%20unchecked%20and%20unabashed%2C%E2%80%9D.%20Gandhi%20then%20stated%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%2C%20therefore%2C%20we%20the%20educated%20and%20the%20semi-educated%20class%20that%20are%20responsible%20for%20the%20hot%20fever%20which%20possessed%20Abdul%20Rashid%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%E2%80%9Csecret%20and%20insidious%20propaganda%E2%80%9D%20caused%20by%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20contagion%20of%20lies%20and%20calumnies%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20newspaper%20man%20of%201926%20has%20been%20multiplied%20manifold%20by%20the%20Godi%20Media%20and%20most%20TV%20channels%2C%20whose%20anchors%20are%20now%20one%20of%20the%20principal%20sources%20of%20the%20hate-filled%20campaign%20against%20people%20based%20on%20the%20religion%20they%20profess.%20Therefore%2C%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20appeal%20for%20boycott%20of%20newspapers%20transmitting%20hatred%20resonates%20in%20INDIA%E2%80%99s%20decision%20not%20to%20send%20their%20representatives%20to%20take%20part%20in%20programmes%20hosted%20by%2014%20TV%20anchors%20who%20are%20accused%20of%20propagating%20a%20hate-driven%20agenda.%20Possibly%20for%20this%20reason%2C%20the%20partners%20described%20their%20decision%20as%20a%20form%20of%20%3Cem%3Esatyagraha%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20non-cooperation%2C%20invoking%20the%20spirit%20of%20the%20freedom%20struggle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ES.N.%20Sahu%20served%20as%20Officer%20on%20Special%20Duty%20to%20President%20of%20India%20K.R.%20Narayanan.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695032459000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F30160235%2FGandhi-1944.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fgandhis-1926-call-for-boycott-of-newspapers-spreading-hatred-resonates-with-indias-decision%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%E2%80%9CIndia%20would%20lose%20nothing%20if%2090%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20papers%20were%20to%20cease%20today%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gandhi%20had%20said%20then.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A65%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fgandhis-1926-call-for-boycott-of-newspapers-spreading-hatred-resonates-with-indias-decision%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22TRAI%20Consultation%20on%20OTT%20Regulation%20Has%20Consequences%20Beyond%20Net%20Neutrality%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F18151637%2Fglenn-carstens-peters-EOQhsfFBhRk-unsplash.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIndia%20is%20rapidly%20digitising.%20There%20are%20good%20things%20and%20bad%2C%20speed-bumps%20on%20the%20way%20and%20caveats%20to%20be%20mindful%20of.%20The%20weekly%20column%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cstrong%3ETerminal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0focuses%20on%20all%20that%20is%20connected%20and%20is%20not%20%E2%80%93%20on%20digital%20issues%2C%20policy%2C%20ideas%20and%20themes%20dominating%20the%20conversation%20in%20India%20and%20the%20world.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.trai.gov.in%2Fconsultation-paper-regulatory-mechanism-over-top-ott-communication-services-and-selective-banning%5C%22%3Econsultation%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Telecom%20Regulatory%20Authority%20of%20India%20(TRAI)%20about%20regulatory%20mechanisms%20for%20Over%20The%20Top%20(OTT)%20communication%20services%20and%20select%20banning%20of%20these%20services%20has%20created%20a%20stir%20around%20net%20neutrality.%20TRAI%20raised%20many%20questions%2C%20one%20being%20the%20impact%20on%20net%20neutrality%20if%20OTTs%20were%20to%20tie%20up%20with%20telecom%20players%20or%20required%20to%20pay%20them%20based%20on%20traffic%20or%20bandwidth.%20Beyond%20net%20neutrality%2C%20this%20consultation%20has%20consequences%20on%20privacy%2C%20encryption%2C%20internet%20shutdowns%20and%20may%20create%20a%20new%20internet%20regime%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETRAI%20has%20been%20requested%20by%20the%20Department%20of%20Telecom%20to%20address%20issues%20around%20regulation%20of%20OTTs%20with%20the%20Parliamentary%20Standing%20Committee%20on%20Communication%20and%20Information%20Technology%E2%80%99s%20recommendations%20on%20selective%20banning%20of%20OTTs%20as%20an%20alternative%20for%20shutdowns.%20This%20has%20effectively%20opened%20up%20a%20host%20of%20issues%20on%20regulation%20of%20OTTs%20under%20the%20telecommunications%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20regards%20to%20the%20issue%20of%20net%20neutrality%2C%20telecom%20service%20providers%20(TSPs)%20in%20India%20want%20OTTs%20to%20pay%20for%20their%20capital%20expenditure%20of%205G%20expansion%20as%20they%20also%20pay%20a%20licensing%20fee%20to%20DoT.%20OTT%20communication%20services%20like%20WhatsApp%2C%20Telegram%2C%20Signal%20and%20other%20apps%20have%20cut%20into%20the%20revenues%20of%20TSPs%20while%20not%20paying%20any%20of%20these%20extra%20licensing%20costs.%20The%20demand%20for%20a%20fee%20from%20OTTs%20to%20pay%20for%20the%20network%20expansion%20is%20considered%20unfair%20when%20customers%20are%20already%20paying%20for%20telecom%20services.%20A%20demand%20for%20any%20form%20of%20network%20fee%20would%20violate%20net%20neutrality%20and%20thus%20will%20limit%20the%20emergence%20of%20new%20OTTs%20by%20giving%20preferential%20treatment%20to%20the%20ones%20paying%20a%20fee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20debate%20around%20net%20neutrality%20was%20settled%20earlier%20with%20the%20fight%20against%20Free%20Basics-Internet.org%20and%20the%20general%20public%20opposition%20to%20Facebook%20becoming%20the%20gatekeeper.%20Those%20conditions%20that%20allowed%20the%20general%20public%20to%20champion%20digital%20rights%20do%20not%20exist%20today%20and%20the%20risk%20of%20net%20neutrality%20being%20repealed%20in%20some%20form%20does%20exist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Government%20of%20India%20has%20been%20actively%20expanding%20regulations%20to%20stop%20Big%20Tech%20firms%E2%80%99%20practices%20and%20has%20been%20actively%20promoting%20Indian%20alternatives.%20Limiting%20Facebook%E2%80%99s%20plans%20around%20the%20internet%20in%20India%20has%20been%20beneficial%20for%20Indian%20startups%20and%20other%20internet%20companies.%20But%20the%20current%20demand%20against%20net%20neutrality%20is%20domestic%2C%20it%20can%20also%20hurt%20Indian%20IT%20firms%20if%20they%20are%20subjected%20to%20the%20same%20regulatory%20setup.%20What%20form%20this%20regulation%20takes%20needs%20to%20be%20seen%2C%20but%20a%20fee%20for%20foreign%20firms%20and%20a%20relaxation%20for%20Indian%20organisations%20in%20some%20measure%20can%20also%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20the%20issue%20of%20net%20neutrality%2C%20it%20is%20the%20issue%20of%20licensing%20conditions%20of%20OTT%20communication%20services%20like%20WhatsApp%20and%20Signal%20that%20will%20be%20most%20concerning.%20The%20demand%20to%20regulate%20OTTs%20is%20coming%20as%20an%20alternative%20solution%20to%20internet%20shutdowns.%20If%20applications%20like%20WhatsApp%2C%20Facebook%20or%20Twitter%20can%20be%20temporarily%20blocked%20during%20emergencies%2C%20then%20there%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20a%20complete%20internet%20shutdown%2C%20is%20the%20argument.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExcept%20one%20can%E2%80%99t%20block%20these%20apps%20temporarily%20and%20the%20only%20way%20to%20do%20this%20would%20be%20to%20build%20a%20Chinese-style%20Great%20Internet%20Firewall%20to%20inspect%20all%20the%20networks%20for%20real-time%20censorship.%20BSNL%20in%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.trai.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FBharat_Sanchar_04092023.pdf%5C%22%3Eresponse%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20consultation%20paper%20has%20concluded%20it%20is%20hard%20to%20ban%20specific%20OTT%20services.%20But%20such%20an%20infrastructure%20can%20technically%20be%20built%20and%20India%E2%80%99s%205G%20telecom%20expansion%20could%20be%20the%20place%20where%20this%20happens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ECurrent%20dimensioning%20of%20TSP%20infrastructure%20had%20not%20envisaged%20such%20type%20of%20deep%20packet%20inspection%20at%20the%20time%20of%20roll%20out%20of%20its%20network.%20Implementation%20of%20selective%20banning%20of%20OTT%20will%20impact%20the%20processing%20power%20of%20resources%20and%20huge%20augmentation%20in%20processing%20power%20will%20be%20required%20at%20TSP%20end.%20It%20is%20pertinent%20to%20mention%20that%20such%20type%20of%20selective%20barring%20can%20be%20done%20for%20limited%20time%20for%20limited%20OTT%20services.%20There%20will%20be%20need%20to%20define%20this%20time%20period%20and%20limit%20of%20number%20of%20OTT%20service%20to%20be%20banned%20at%20a%20time%2C%20this%20will%20help%20to%20designing%20and%20expanding%20the%20TSP%20infrastructure%20accordingly%3C%2Fem%3E.%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20BSNL%20response%20on%20selective%20banning%20of%20OTTs%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20aspect%20of%20this%20regulation%20is%20also%20how%20it%20will%20regulate%20end-to-end%20encrypted%20systems%20for%20internal%20security%20requirements.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.trai.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FGloba_%2520Encryption_Coalition_Steering_01092023.pdf%5C%22%3EGlobal%20Encryption%20Coalition%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20concerned%20with%20TRAI%E2%80%99s%20plans%20for%20regulation%20of%20OTTs%20and%20the%20consequences%20on%20encryption.%20At%20present%2C%20Section%2069%20of%20the%20Information%20Technology%20Act%20does%20give%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20powers%20to%20intercept%20and%20decrypt%20encrypted%20content.%20For%20a%20long%20time%20the%20question%20of%20WhatsApp%20encryption%20and%20the%20need%20to%20identify%20the%20contents%20of%20messages%20spreading%20hate%20and%20misinformation%20has%20been%20debated%20in%20our%20courts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20TRAI%20consultation%20recommendations%20will%20determine%20whether%20India%20adopts%20a%20new%20telecom%20regime.%20This%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20we%20have%20opened%20these%20conversations%2C%20but%20with%20the%20new%20Telecom%20Bill%20likely%20to%20be%20tabled%20in%20the%20parliament%2C%20these%20consultations%20will%20determine%20the%20fate%20of%20Indians%20digital%20rights.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdot.gov.in%2Frelatedlinks%2Findian-telecommunication-bill-2022%5C%22%3Edraft%20Indian%20Telecommunications%20Bill%202022%3C%2Fa%3E%20already%20has%20several%20provisions%20concerning%20the%20TRAI%E2%80%99s%20present%20consultation%2C%20some%20of%20those%20provisions%20are%20expected%20to%20change%20before%20it%20is%20introduced%20in%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20host%20of%20these%20regulatory%20demands%20will%20likely%20be%20implemented%20in%20Manipur%20with%20the%20near%20complete%20internet%20shutdown%20in%20the%20state.%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20road%20towards%20access%20to%20the%20internet%20could%20likely%20be%20with%20new%20OTT%20regulations%2C%20with%20no%20interest%20from%20any%20quarters%20to%20address%20the%20challenges%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20India%20does%20push%20for%20regulation%20of%20OTTs%20registration%20in%20India%20or%20presses%20for%20additional%20costs%20for%20operations%2C%20several%20international%20companies%20are%20likely%20to%20exit%20the%20market.%20This%20is%20what%20happened%20when%20India%20brought%20its%20VPN%20rules%20asking%20VPN%20companies%20to%20maintain%20logs.%20One%20can%20term%20it%20going%20back%20to%20the%20licence%20raj%20era%2C%20with%20the%20increased%20regulations%20that%20are%20already%20under%20development%20limiting%20imports%20of%20computers%2C%20telecom%20equipment%20into%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fskodali%5C%22%3ESrinivas%20Kodali%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20researcher%20on%20digitisation%20and%20a%20hacktivist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695031242000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F18151637%2Fglenn-carstens-peters-EOQhsfFBhRk-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Ftrai-consultation-on-ott-regulation-has-consequences-beyond-net-neutrality%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Beyond%20the%20issue%20of%20net%20neutrality%2C%20it%20is%20the%20issue%20of%20licensing%20conditions%20of%20OTT%20communication%20services%20like%20WhatsApp%20and%20Signal%20that%20will%20be%20most%20concerning.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Ftrai-consultation-on-ott-regulation-has-consequences-beyond-net-neutrality%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22MotoGP%20Bharat%20expected%20to%20create%20an%20impact%20of%20over%20Rs%20950%20crore%20in%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695031185000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-09%2F18%2Ffull%2F1695030817-1589.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fsports%2Fother-sports-news%2Fmotogp-bharat-expected-to-create-an-impact-of-over-rs-950-crore-in-india-123091800525_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20an%20interview%20with%20Business%20Standard%2C%20the%20promoter%20of%20the%20event%20said%20that%20from%20now%20Buddh%20International%20Circuit%20will%20be%20able%20to%20accommodate%20both%20F1%20and%20MotoGP%20racing%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fsports%2Fother-sports-news%2Fmotogp-bharat-expe