en%20started%20to%20skip%20school%20to%20do%20daily%20wage%20work.%20We%20decided%20to%20employ%20these%20kids%20in%20the%20school%20and%20pay%20them%20so%20that%20they%20would%20attend%20school%2C%E2%80%9D%20Parmita%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CAs%20the%20students%20upgrade%20to%20a%20higher%20class%2C%20we%20employ%20the%20suitable%20ones%20to%20teach%20the%20lower%20classes%20under%20supervision.%20For%20this%20service%2C%20we%20pay%20them.%20This%20way%2C%20our%20kids%20have%20the%20motivation%20to%20study%20well%20and%20become%20%E2%80%98student%20teachers%E2%80%99%20and%20earn%20pocket%20money%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20model%20helped%20them%20gain%20more%20attendance.%20%E2%80%9CBy%20the%20end%20of%202016%2C%20we%20had%20around%20200%20students%20waiting%20to%20get%20admission%20in%20the%20school%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20model%20worked%20well%20for%20the%20school%2C%20Parmita%20observed%20that%20parents%20were%20taking%20money%20from%20their%20children%E2%80%99s%20earnings%20for%20personal%20expenses%2C%20including%20buying%20liquor.%20To%20address%20this%20issue%2C%20the%20school%20decided%20to%20replace%20cash%20with%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20point%2C%20for%20example%2C%2050%20points%20represent%20Rs%2050%2C%20ensuring%20that%20the%20funds%20are%20spent%20solely%20on%20the%20child%E2%80%99s%20needs.%20The%20school%20also%20partnered%20with%20local%20shops%20selling%20sweets%20and%20garments%20to%20allow%20students%20to%20use%20their%20points%20there.%20The%20school%20management%20then%20settles%20the%20bills%20on%20their%20behalf%20in%20cash.%20This%20system%20has%20safeguarded%20students%20and%20their%20hard-earned%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%